You're not the first one, Selena. You're not the first woman he's used up and thrown away. For years I'd been hearing this Faith Seed was tall as her brother, with black hair. Couldn't miss her. And then I saw you in one of their trucks last week, yellow hair in the breeze, and heard them calling you Faith. He thinks he can just SWAP YOU OUT. Like you don't got a brain of your own. God knows who you are, and so do you. Selena, I love you. Don't lose yourself to this.

Lana. Christ in heaven what they did to you. The fact they could make you believe all that nonsense, make you forget yourself so hard. Forget your own name? How, Lana? What did he say to you? What kind of fucking dirtbag blood ritual could make you think your name was "Faith"? Doesn't matter how, I guess. He told you you were special, but in the end he threw your body in here to disintegrate in the boiling muck, like a common Angel.
Former US camp which was overrun by the NVA.

An act of God took the lives of 16 people in this very hotel and they want me to believe there isn't a SINGLE GHOST HERE. Sure. This whole county is completely eerie. There's even this wacky cult that owns some of the businesses. Funny little dudes and dudettes. Hot Springs Hotel is just dripping with paranormal activity - the ectoplasm is even manifesting as mist! I can't believe no one else in my circles has stumbled on this place. I bet you I can get on TV if I contact the right people! Who am I gonna call?

I know this is hard. It hurts to hurt. But we're giving the unbelievers a last chance to tell us how to save our project, to save everything. They want to help. They just need pain to give them permission to betray the people they think are their friends. Don't worry, the bliss will wash away your pain when you've finished serving the Father this way. With love, Your Priestess

In the cave behind the bush, I got what you asked for.
It isn't much, but it's all I could scavenge.
I can't stay here, it's too exposed. I'm going to try and save as many people as I can.
Good luck.

Our new angels may be lost when they first enter the Bliss.
Welcome them. Guide them. Give them their calling.
You are an extension of Faith and she is counting on you.
Main Command Post in this area.

The only ghost I believe in is the holy ghost, alright? If there were any spirits in the hotel, they're HOLY spirits, who're going to help us take the Henbane river. I swear to the Father himself if I get one more of you coming to me quivering about weird noises in the hotel I'm going to send you back to Faith to be redistributed. Angels ain't afraid of no ghosts. And we could always use more angels.

Dear sir or madam, Here is my revised manuscript for FRANKIE SINCLAIR'S FRENCH FOODSTUFFS MADE EASY. I'll have you know my cooking delights hundreds of dozens of people at King’s Hot Springs Hotel. I got the letter that said not to submit again, but you guys are my top choice. I know you'll love it this time. Bon appetite! Chef Frankie

By now I'm in Cuba. Less red tape bullshit and no goddamn Seed family! I'll put my megadump where people appreciate it! Take whatever you want, I got my insurance claim already. Fuck this country. --Dodd

Brothers, It's time to pull the tanks from storage. We'll begin gradually adding the Bliss to the water reservoir, starting with ten tanks per day for one week, and adjusting accordingly based on the effects. This process will be long and grueling, but we must remain patient and optimistic. It will work. We will save the lives of those who cannot save their own. This is what the Father wants.
There is so much work to be done with so little time. Eden's Gate views Sloth as an unaffordable luxury that is contemptuous to God.)

Frobisher was a local mountain lion who was a pain in the ass. He'd eat livestock and pets. He mauled a 7 year old boy. He outsmarted every hunter that ever tried to take him down. Then one day, Frobisher ate the star pitcher of the rival baseball team and became a hero. The grateful people re-named their team the Hope County Cougars in his honor. God bless you, Frobisher.

After your wife and child left this Earth we feared for your life. We feared that you had let the weakness overtake you. But you did not. You became the hunter and not the hunted. You gave up sin. You gave up vice and all the evil that had overrun your life. We put our hands upon you and together we took away your sin. We cut it from your chest, just as every member here has also given up their sin.
Some sinner's locked the door. I can't break into it from this side. I'm gonna go across the water and try and shoot the lock off. It's a one in a million shot, but I got what it takes.
Out of gas, out of hope.

Let me ask you something. You see any kids around here? Don’t you think that’s strange? I’ve been talkin’ about it for years, but nobody listens. You know why that is? Baby Farms. It’s all the rage in silicon valley. They’re growing babies just to harvest them for body parts. I’ve seen it with my own eyes. Elon Musk has his personal farm half hour north of here. Terrifying stuff. Even worse is what they do with the unhealthy babies. The unhealthy ones are sent to the pits. The ultra elite love to gamble on baby pit fights. They attach little scalpels to their tiny hands and the babies have a Battle Royale until only one stands. I wouldn’t have believed it myself, if I didn’t discover the boxscores coded in Oprah’s book club. Those poor poor babies.

I never had much faith in the system but this is ridiculous. When I was growing up the locals owned their businesses. One of the perks of living way out here is that no big corporations have their fingers in our shit. Nowadays this Seed family owns almost every damned thing in the valley. Moved in silently like a cancer. That family's just about as nice and friendly as the biggest oil corporation you can imagine. Might as well move back to Misoula.

The Father once told me "No one believes death is coming until the moment it does. And most still refuse to believe it even then." But after everything I witnessed with Mary May and her brother. I believe it. God forgive me.
A WWII-era SMG. It was nicknamed the "luxury car of submachine guns" because of Its high quality.
This pump-action shotgun will cause more internal damage than cheap vodka.
This SMG is proud of its rapid fire, low recoil, and Czechoslovakian roots.
This semiautomatic became part of the U.S. Armed forces in 1985. It's a millennial, so... you know.
This handgun with muzzle fire and burst fire is the choice of all cybernetic organisms who enter the force.
This mass produced bolt action rifle with scope is sold in discount department stores and proudly made in the U.S.A.
Strong and durable, this rod is perfect for anyone new to fly fishing.
Do you think this is still one of the most powerful handguns in the world? Well, do ya, punk?
A baseball bat made of wood. Classic. Used for more than just hitting balls.
This Italian semi-automatic shotgun brings new meaning to the phrase “talking with your hands.”
Death, taxes, and the 1911. The design of this American made semi automatic hasn't changed since WWI.
A 527 Carbine that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
A 1887 that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
A dependable handgun used by many state police departments. It's about as American as Swiss Cheese.
A long-handled gardening tool with a thin metal blade. ...And, your mom.
A brutal clubbing weapon. It's the love child of the sporting goods and the hardware aisles.
This bow is the non-firearm weapon of choice for highly skilled Green Berets from Vietnam.
This semi-automatic's sleek design and accuracy, make this the pistol of choice by countless Hollywood villains.
This .50 cal semi-auto rifle has solid stopping power. If it does that for more than 4 hours, call a doctor.
This accurate semi-auto sniper rifle was tested under countless conditions. It's ready for the post post apocalypse.
The short barreled modern M133 wants you to know that length isn’t as important as the spread of shot.
A powerful handgun that is perfect for close quarters self defense.
This sawed-off shotgun has seen its share of wastelands. It's brutal. It's effective. Enough said.
This compound bow is for those who are into that game and wildlife look.
Designed to deliver severe damage to your victim, while protecting your fingers.
The cult's flamethrower used for destroying material possessions of sinners.
This revolver is guaranteed to get you out of dirty and/or hairy situations.
Instructions for using this belt-fed machine gun are: apply red bandana, pull trigger, and yell.
A victim of the housing collapse who changed careers late in life to become a weapon.
The modern version of the AK-47. It has been used by armies, militias, and radical groups around the world.
A weapon from the primal days with a very low carbon footprint.
This subcompact machine pistol will burn through bullets faster than a fake news story gets shared.
Use this to propel yourself in a boat or stir a giant vat of chili.
A Compound Bow that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
This is not your father’s tactical rifle. It’s lightweight, shoots a high caliber bullet, and instead of smoking, it vapes.
Coveted by collectors, this WWII era SMG was more reliable than its American counterpart.
The modern version of the AK-47 designed for close quarters combat. Don’t bring up the size thing.
This 9mm SMG's cousin is the AK-47. They can marry each other and not have weird looking offspring.
This SMG is a veteran of the silver screen who seriously deserves a lifetime achievement award.
This hand cannon is a huge action film star and deserves a star on the walk of fame.
It does one thing and one thing only… it shoots a steady stream of fire. Pro Tip: Don’t burn yourself.
A while ago, this pipe was part of an anonymous leak. The bosses found out and it lost its job.
A mid-ranged fly fishing rod with a high gauge line and a fast reel.
Ever had the fantasy of delivering an artillery strike with just a trigger pull? This grenade launcher is for you.
The classic .45 caliber semi-automatic with an extended barrel. To this one, length means accuracy (and coolness).
This Cold War-era pistol with detachable suppressor was made for wetwork. (It's also a grower, not a shower.)
This 1911 has a red bold color scheme that screams "I knew this was going to happen!"
This SMG has an extremely high rate of fire. It burns through ammo faster than you can scroll through a newsfeed.
The inventor of this dependable assault rifle believed it to be “a weapon of defense and not a weapon of offense.”
Once a military oddball, this modular semi-automatic rifle has become wildly popular with the DIY crowd.
A 1911 that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
A tool with a broad flat blade used for moving earth, snow, or bullshit in the workplace.
This launcher lets you guide rockets by aiming. Neat!
Jacob Seed’s bolt action .50 cal sniper rifle. You'll need to use it a lot to change the name of this one.
This traditional lever-action shotgun is a must for cowboys and brawny time-traveling assassin robots.
This SMG loves close-quarters combat. The more restrictive, the better. You’ll hear a safe word if it has a problem.
This tactical grade .45 cal lever action rifle was designed for law enforcement and usually sleeps in police stations.
This .50 cal bolt action rifle knows about accuracy and penetration. Just like your sarcastic "friend."
A reliable 1911 with a aerial color scheme. Shooting for the sky will be that much easier with this.
A M133 that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
A semi-automatic rifle manufactured to maintain long distance relationships, or eliminating them.
This has made countless slow-pitch softball players feel like first ballot hall of famers.
This shotgun knows the flavors of sin. Delicious.
This is the modern version of the M133. It will cause more internal damage than REALLY cheap vodka.
Why use your arm to throw grenade, when you can just pull a trigger? Perfect for short to mid-range targets.
This full-auto machine pistol did a couple seasons of a Miami crime TV drama in the 80s. It still gets residuals.
A double barreled shotgun with tremendous stopping power. It's also been part of a couple quick weddings.
The ultimate version of the cult's flamethrower that's used for ceremonies.
This classic .45 cal lever action rifle was designed for hunting and usually rests inside of a cabin in the woods.
A lightweight tactical rifle that is so good at close-quarters combat it can sometimes get a bit creepy.
A powerful handgun + a longer barrel = what do you think?
The M133 pump-action shotgun with better handling ...and a Napoleon complex.
An AK-47 that celebrates a Far Cry® classic.
A wooden paddle for rowing or braining. If you're going up Shit’s Creek, bring this.
A reliable SMG with a suppressor. Just like someone you’re having an affair with, they will keep it discreet.
The easy to use/hard to master weapon of juvenile delinquents, game hunters, and guerrilla forces.
Do you think this is still one of the most powerful handguns in the world? Well, do ya, punk?
This workhorse of a machine gun has seen action in every U.S. conflict since ‘89 and is considering retirement.
This mass produced RPG launcher is everywhere. No need to camp outside of a store for a midnight launch.
These knives are perfect for hitting a human target (combat) or not hitting a human target (circus/sideshow act).
One of six possible murder weapons you'd find in a mansion. "Whodunit?" is the real question.
This bow uses a pulley & cam system to give the archer a mechanical advantage. It's not cheating.
This weapon uses some kind of magnetized microwaves that, if aimed properly, can explode organic targets. WTF?
This top quality submachine gun is used by those who protect the White House and Vatican City.
This sawed-off shotgun has seen its share of wastelands. It's brutal. It's effective. Enough said.
The modern version of the AK-47. It has been used by armies, militias, and radical groups around the world.
An MP5K painted in a way that would make the founding fathers of America get teary eyed.
Top of the line professional fly fishing rod with good line strength and superior reel speed.
A professional quality fly fishing rod with the best line strength and good reel speed.
Do you want to replay this map?
Top quality fly for catching the biggest salmon. (Kokanee, Chinook, Arctic Greyling, etc.)
This lure will attracts bigger Pallid Sturgeon, Paddlefish, and maybe a trophy to bring home.
Wanna get some bass? This fly attracts big fish. (Small Mouth, Large Mouth, Rock, etc.)
Best fly for catching all kinds of trout. (Golden, Bull, Lake, Rainbow, etc.)
This versatile fly is a staple of tackle boxes everywhere. You can catch any fish with this.
Eden's Gate has taken over this marina and is using it as a launch spot for their water convoys.
Eden's Gate converted the Stone Ridge Chalet into a training ground for new cult recruits.
Eden's Gate is hoarding fruits and vegetables and is packing them onto trucks headed for their bunkers.
Eden's Gate has taken over this cattle farm and is slaughtering the cows for their meat.
Eden's Gate is starting the process of turning their harvested flowers into their signature drug: The Bliss.
Eden's Gate is stripping the metal off of old trains to fortify their bunkers.
Eden's Gate has claimed the Baron Lumber Mill and is holding captured prisoners there until they are ready for Jacob's indoctrination.
Eden's Gate is transforming the processed flowers into their final form: The Bliss.
Eden's Gate has taken over the animal sanctuary and is using it to keep captured wolves before sending them off to Elk Jaw Lodge.
The devoted can rest here during their pilgrimages as they walk The Path to Eden's Gate.
Eden's Gate has taken all the gas from this location and is running their convoys through here.
Eden's Gate has transformed an old missile silo into a bunker to protect them from the Collapse.
Eden's Gate has transformed this old camp into a field of flowers that will eventually become The Bliss drug.
Eden's Gate is using the abandoned military radar station to keep an eye on the forest and maintain air superiority in the area.
Eden's Gate is using this park lodge to perform experiments that can change wolves into monstrosities called "Judges".
Eden's Gate is hoarding fruits and vegetables and is packing them onto trucks headed for their bunkers.
Eden's Gate has taken over this estate and transformed it into a research & development lab for The Bliss.
Eden's Gate is transforming the factory's fertilizer into dangerous explosives.
The Project at Eden's Gate has taken over the heart of the Valley.
What could Eden's Gate possibly want with this old, abandoned hotel?
Eden's Gate has taken over the Ranger's Station and is using it as a place to train and supply their soldiers.
Eden's Gate has taken over this church, where they prepare their captives for baptisms.
Eden's Gate is using the Gardenview Packing Facility to send the orchard's fruit to their bunkers.
Eden's Gate has taken the local garage in order to create and maintain their many convoys.
John's property contains a private airfield and is heavily guarded at all times.

If a US soldier finds this, send it with my dogtags to MACV I was captured while on operations and held for approximately 10 days. I sustained combat injuries and was further injured when I escaped. For the record, I saw instances of prisoners being pushed into crocodile infested waters. My strength is gone and I am not going to make it any further than this hut. Tell my wife I love her.

Oregano in a sandwich bag. Give these stems & seeds to Hurk and he will light up a couple more cultists.
Stick this in your cap and call it "macaroni."

Deputy I think it's time we should talk. Come meet me at Redtail cabin.
- Eli

It's all gone. The savings, the stocks, the house. I can't face Cynthia, or the kids. I told them we're going camping, but there's nothing to go home to. Oh God, please forgive me.
Greg Clagette
WARNING Don't go near the Reaves Forest Park. The Church has the entrance guarded with armed guards and are turning away any "unbelievers". If you value your life you'll stay far away.
Reminder: Head over to the Ranger Station to pick up more rifle ammo. We're running low after the last training exercise.

Carl
I've got another batch of recruits ready for boot camp at the Chalet. Kyle shows a lot of promise, but Ben could be trouble so keep an eye on him.
Stuart

If you're ever up hunting by Snowshoe lake keep an eye out for the Hunting Shelter. I left you a little something.
Ted

Eli
I'm worried about how safe we really are in these woods. I've got my family staying at Merlin Cabin, but I don't know for how long.
Keep out of trouble
Tim Noble

Stuart Remember, Jacob doesn't want anybody shooting any wolves. Tell your boys they need to be captured and brought to the Elk Jaw Lodge. There's a reward for every animal delivered, a bonus if they haven't been harmed.
Roy

Kevin When you have more security dogs trained be sure to send them up to the Radar Station. We've had some unbelievers nosing around and we need to increase patrols to keep them out.
Carl
Prevent the execution of Specialist Boyd.
Save the sole survivor of the farming village.
He’s slippery, don’t let him get away.
Save the prisoner who is being held in the river warehouse.
Deny the enemy use of this weapon.
Save the prisoner being held at a farm, but watch for banteng.
This guy deserves whatever he gets.
Take out the gun, save a pilot’s life.
Kill the Colonel with extreme prejudice.
Knock out the enemy’s air defenses.
Help Moses get back to his family.
Save the POW before he becomes crocodile food.
Kill the Colonel and his soldiers.
Save Pfc. Chavez before it’s too late.
Protect the village from further harm.
Silence this gun any way you can.

NAME OF APPLICANT: Thomson Salvage & Recovery LOCATION: Silver Lake, Montana DESCRIPTION: Small Cessna, submerged NOTES: "The Spirit" along with pilot Fred Tanner went down March 8, 2013 Recovered a lockbox from the fuselage. Key to lockbox still missing.

Ian, My dear, if you're reading this you must think I've abandoned you. The crash knocked you out cold, and nothing I did could wake you up. I didn’t want to leave you, but I have to go find help. The Cult's watching the roads but I think there's a way up by the falls. There's no way I can carry the lockbox but I got the key with me so those fuckers can't open it.
Don't worry, I'll be back soon. Love always, Ted

Sorry I locked you out, but I just couldn't wait. I heard some noises outside the cabin and just had to follow. If you need your gear, just head north along the trail, I'm up at the old lookout. I've got a feeling our hunt is over soon and we'll have proof of that squatch once and for all! Get the drams ready!
Dicky Dansky

Eli has tasked me with finding a way to get the message out. The cult controls all communications, not to mention all the bridges in and out. Our only hope is to fly out before they are able to control the skies as well. I’ve got my gear with me, I plan on leaving tonight under cover of darkness. Wish me luck. -Kyle

I can't believe it! There is no way these tracks are man-made. I followed them all the way up to the lookout point, but then the trail goes cold. My best option is to stay here and see if I can maybe catch a glimpse of the squatch that made 'em. Fingers crossed.
Dicky Dansky

For fuck's sake Russ, you broke the damn generator again. How the hell am I supposed to open the door and get the plane out now?
I'm off to get Shep to come and fix it. And I swear to God that if you left the skylight open again I'm going to fire your ass.
- Ben

I can't believe it! I heard it! A genuine sasquatch call! I'm sure it's from a cave I've seen on the nearby cliffs. I've got a feeling that today is going to be the day that I come face to face with the squatch itself!

To: Shep
Damn thief got into my cabin, nearly got my stash. I'm off to track that bastard down. Meanwhile see what you can do with the lock. I'll be damned if this is going to happen again.
-Hardcastle

Tanner, Got orders from Jacob to remove Elliot and his family from their house. They've been a thorn in our ass for far too long. Make sure you check their bunker, they could be hiding in there. Use whatever means necessary. - Billy

The Golden Path has taken to enlisting the intelligent macaques in Kyrat as there are no more suitable recruits left in the region. Surely, it is a sign that the Golden Path is desperate.
The pig roots around in the mud and wallows in its own filth. It is thankful to be slaughtered and eaten, for only then does it have a higher purpose as food and fuel for the Royal Army's cause.
Ancient and feared, this great hunter has not evolved in millennia because it's been perfect for so long; it proves that the truth does not need to be perfected or embellished.
Known mostly for their sweet and succulent meat, wild boar are vicious creatures and should be avoided unless absolutely necessary, or when preparing breakfast fit for King Min.
Within the year, all white-chested bears will be painted pink to honor our great king and fearless leader, Pagan Min.
The Monal scurries around with no direction and it isn't a smart animal. It is easy prey for predators, not unlike the citizens of Kyrat in the face of the dangerous Golden Path.

After the failure of a reality show featuring this rare rhino, the Karkadann fled into the Kyrati bush. Now it only makes rare appearances to forage for food or drink from a cool pool when it thinks no one is looking.
Belief in the Ghost Bear constitutes superstition and will not be tolerated. The attack that left army soldiers mutilated and mauled was orchestrated by terrorists in large bear costumes.

While the appearance of the Tibetan wolf may be alarming, Kyrati residents can take comfort in the knowledge they will only meet one if they have been placed under arrest. Any other mention of encounters, such as those in the wild, are false.
His armored hide impenetrable like Paul’s fortress, the rhinoceros is peaceful when left alone but he will charge with deadly strength and brandish his fearsome horn when threatened.

Like our beloved King Pagan Min, the Yak is a beacon of power and working tirelessly for the people of Kyrat. A shining example of the self-sacrifice and commitment to the greater good that our King himself has brought to this great nation.

The Kyrati Tiger shares many traits with the distinguished Governor Yuma, an elegant guardian who strikes without mercy against her enemies. But to the people of Kyrat, she is the loving mother who nurtures and protects her cubs.

This slow animal can be seen sunning itself on rocks and scurrying away at the slightest provocation or danger. It's cowardice and laziness is not unlike the Golden Path terrorists who want everything for nothing.

This rare fish is named after the dark waters it prefers to lay its eggs in. Black Water Dragons are actually albino. They are prized by our great Governors for its part in extracting useful information from terrorists.

The snow leopard is among the most regal and elegant of all cats, its image so glorious that it rivals that of our beloved King Min. Therefore, should one cross your path, you should shoot the snow leopard on sight.

Some citizens claim that crows hold the reincarnated souls of all citizens who died trying to fight King Min. While the Ministry of Social Harmony cannot endorse such superstitions, it thanks its citizens for such loving beliefs.
The guardian of Kyrat, strong and noble like our King. He roams the countryside bringing luck and good fortune to all he passes, and he bows in the presence of our King Pagan Min.

The rare and beautiful Sky Tiger will continue to rule over the wilds of Kyrat just as our gracious King Min rules over our civilized lands. Should any citizen fall prey to the Sky Tiger, know that it would have been the same justice meted out by King Min.
In the noble beehive, nature mimics King Min’s vision for Kyrat: Co-operative and efficient, they are willing to attack any aggressors in times of war when their leader is threatened.
A wild dog remains a wild dog, regardless of whether you give it a name or not. Report any sightings of Tenzin to your nearest Royal Army officer for immediate action so the creature can be put down.

The demon fish that swim in Kyrat's waters are silent and unseen until they sense someone disloyal to King Min. Then, they react, stripping the flesh from the bone before the traitor can offer any regret or contrition.
Pagan Min has decreed that pit viper meat is safe for consumption. He has a cook dedicated to the preparation of pit viper stew and he enjoys adding pit viper meat in his Crab Rangoon.
Among honey badgers, Gulo is the most rare and feared of them all. Some say he is the grandfather of all honey badgers, but everyone knows the one true father of all things in Kyrat is King Min.
Faithful assistants to our fighting men, these dogs were not even trained; they saw fit to carry themselves with discipline and precision because they were so inspired by Pagan Min's cause.

While most elephants never forget, this thick skinned rarity also has a penchant for vengeance. Pagan Min’s Sector for the Use of Abusive Animals is looking into harnessing these vengeful qualities, but until then, residents are warned to stay away.
This strange and unique creature was not native to Kyrat until King Min decided that the people deserved to have this storybook animal roam their wilderness, and made his will reality.

The tapir is a large, awkward animal that lumbers through the forest, seemingly without direction and easy prey for tigers and stronger animals. It is a reminder to our loyal citizens that some animals exist to feed the kingdom.
Thanks to King Min’s generous distribution of hand-held mirrors, Shadow Leopard attacks from behind have decreased by over 70 percent. This fact is brought to you by the Society for Social Harmony.
The tenacious honey badger displays the fighting spirit of the Royal Guard with its unwillingness to quit, its relentlessness against foes, and cunning in the face of adversity.

The Ministry of Animal Control declares the sambar a large vermin, and encourages the slaughter of these animals. The flesh of the sambar is unhealthy and unwholesome because it rubs itself in its own urine-soaked soil.

Slow of foot, but hard of shell, one can easily see the similarities between the red crowned turtle and the Golden Path. A grenade stuffed down the throat, however, is more than sufficient when dealing with both.

As with common wolves, Kyrati residents need not fear an encounter unless they find themselves behind the bars of a Royal Army prison. Unlike regular wolves, the Mad Devil delivers a dose of insanity with each bite.

This cat is at home in the rugged terrain of Kyrat. Mountain or river, it climbs trees and hides in tall grass, serving as an example to the Royal Army that nothing should ever block them from their goal.

Starting immediately, all white rumped vultures are to be re-colored pink to honor our great king and fearless leader, Pagan Min. Re-coloring of the vulture rumps will be delegated to Kyrati citizens as thanks for their King.
As long as Kyrat is split in two, stray dogs will continue to wander, lost and alone. Only when the Golden Path threat is ended can King Min unite all orphans into one family.
This majestic and noble creature watches over the land, all-seeing from the greatest of heights, reminding us that we, too, must remain vigilant for our freedom.
The bharals started migrating north over the King's Bridge when King Min first blessed Kyrat with his guidance. They preferred the sweeter grass in the north over the rotting vegetation in the south.
Thanks to the efforts of the Ministry of Animal Control, there are no rats in Kyrat. Anyone who sees a rat in Kyrat is mistaken and will face disciplinary action.

Any other person...and I use that word sparingly with Angels, would get sick of all that repetitive labour. Angels are happy to carry Bliss barrels from the brewery, everywhere, back and forth, all damned day. Divine chemical. Just divine.

Mr. Marvel, This letter is to inform you that your request to film at the Grimalkin Radon Mine has been refused. Your application contained insufficient administrative information for our response to be considered. Furthermore, the Commission cannot approve requests which may endanger the lives of any professionals engaged in filming. As the location remains radioactive, we cannot condone prolonged exposure of workers to its environment. We invite you to propose alternative sites within Hope County for your project. Regards, The Hope County Film Commission

To everyone looking for me,
The end of the world is coming. The global financial system is going to fall apart and the only person preparing for it is Joseph Seed.
The Project doesn't talk in financial terms, but it's the Collapse all the same. Real estate will plummet, businesses will fail, no one's going to regulate anything... and Eden's Gate knows the real cause of all this: Greed. It's the root of all our problems. For once, I've met like-minded people.
They're hunkering down until it all blows over. If you care for your future, you'll join us.
- Melvin Adams Abercrombie
1. Move out of Grampa Melvin's basement. 2. Make my way to Grampa Colin's place. 3. Find the comics he promised me. 3a. Try not to get killed by the cult.

Kids,
Don't worry about me, I've got family here. A new family called Eden's Gate. One day you can join me. Faith showed me that selling her my shop would set me free from my stresses. It's honest work, with people who look out for each other. Don't you fret.
Nolan.

I think the Angels like being next to all the best stuff down here. They're happy to stay down here and guard it in the damp, bless their hides. It's like a cupboard that defends itself. So don't fret about leaving Angels to guard our stash. Lord knows there can always be more Angels.

No humans were harmed in the making of this film. What you see are exceptional special effects employing body doubles we code-named "angels." They are 100% excluded from any human rights commission coverage. This film is in full compliance with board regulations etc etc. (Get lawyer to jazz up lingo.) Sincerely, Guy Marvel

The processed flowers we receive from the camp have to be distilled into something better. We've repurposed an old brewery, a place made for gluttony, addiction, a springboard for sin. The Bliss cleanses our souls, and the Project cleanses the real world. All is as it should be.

I don't understand why it takes you so long to give your tithe of fruits and vegetables to the project. You have a perfectly good trailer just sitting next to your garage. Attach it to your truck and MOVE IT. John's patience has limits, Mike. You don't want to see him get mad.

I have one question for you. Just one. In the future, do you think humanity will look back on this time with pride? Do you think history will record this as a time of peace, caring, and compassion? The future is watching. We are out there looking back. And WE HERE NOW in THIS MOMENT have been CHOSEN. Let the future bear witness to our actions.
I AM YOUR FATHER. YOU ARE MY CHILDREN TOGETHER WE WILL MARCH TO EDEN’S GATE.

Agenda this week: Hurry the harvest. John needs to run a convoy soon so we'd better have those baskets ready. Remember, our survival depends on having all this food safe in John's Gate before the Collapse.
A note from Mary May's father
Note placeholder description for the NOTE #3 of D2_MEGA_01
When Orville Fall struck gold, his small mining camp quickly grew. Decades later, his rival, baron Emmett Reaves shot him dead in the streets, giving the town its name.

I’m sorry that I’m having such a hard time lately putting this all behind me. I just don’t know how to move forward. It’s so hard when I hear from you, and it’s harder when I don’t. I feel like I’m just waiting for that day when I can see you again – but then what? It’ll be back to the same old thing. I really want things to be okay, except I can’t figure out what that is for me. And I don’t expect you to know. All I know is that what we have isn’t love. And it has to stop. -Joy

We're stopping work. No more repairs, not even an oil check. John's been around with his Chosen. Don't worry about your job, I'm not firing anybody over this. I'll pay you what I can in the meantime, but stay safe. If that means being at the garage, fine. If that means being at home, that's fine too. Just don't come around because you think you have to. Something's up.

You promised me you'd keep the guns away from the kids. Guess who had to tidy them up and put them in the locker downstairs. Again.

If the cult shows up, I want you getting out of there. You understand? No trying to fight 'em off. You're not trained for that, and it's just a store. I'm not willing to lose a one of you to those assholes. So, the cult shows, and you run. That's an order. Red
My brother only wants the dogs that are worthy. Sort the wheat from the chaff, then send the strongest ones to the North. -John

Fall’s End is free, but Eden's Gate stole most of the town's food. Gotta hand it to the bastard: John made a brilliant tactical move. Without proper nutrition, we won't have the energy to fight. Sounds like an afterthought,until you feel the pain of hunger. It's a hindrance, and adrenaline can only fuel you for so long. I'm sure I can scavenge some scraps and provide something of substance for a little while, but there's a difference between being full and being sated. It's psychological. I need to bring back the Testy Festy. It's the only way to guarantee both a full belly and a fighting spirit.

The cult must have followed us to this mine. We threw up some makeshift barricades and dug in for a firefight, but they sent down... I don't know who or what these Peggies are, but they're monsters. We keep shootin' them, but they keep getting back up. We can't call for help down here. God help us all.

The orders for the reaping of this abandoned mine are as follows: Collect any tools left behind. Salvage all mining equipment and scrap metal. Test functionality of batteries and electrical equipment. Mine whatever ore veins are left. *Crate and guard contents until reaping vehicles arrive.

You know how I know Eden’s Gate is connected to the government? They’re not even hiding their god damn playbook. They’re drugging the livestock, vegetables, and water just like they always do. Only now they’re testing a new formula. It’s not enough to be docile. They want a mindless braindead workforce to do their bidding. If we don’t stop them here and now, they’ll spread bliss to all of mankind.

Funny how it's always the little blowtorch that makes the peggies talk. Think I have all the info I need now. I'll share: They seem to be taking reaped people to the east first, to brainwash them. If you're missing family, you might try there. I'm going to go find them. Might be the last thing I do, but that's ok.

Walk around the animal and do an initial visual check. It is imperative you get this data BEFORE subject is sedated and shipped to the Lodge. Wounds – Are there any visible and open wounds? Temperament – Is the animal still aggressive, or are they lethargic? Age – How old is the animal? Remember, too young or too old and the treatment won’t take. Make sure this information is given to the Scientists at the Lodge upon delivery.

Don't get me wrong, this is a shit nightmare hell of a situation... But before? I was going fucking crazy. Wringing my hands and feeding my ulcers while I watched our country go down the can. "Use your vote", yeah, sure, like my state let me vote LAST time. Under THESE circumstances though? I see a bunch of assholes hurting people, I know I CAN do something. We can camp out by the path and run ambushes - stop these fucked up pilgrimages. We can REALLY resist.

I taste the Bliss all the time in the back of my throat. Like sweet ashes. It's all the air tastes like. I'm not even hungry anymore I just want More of it. Christ. I won't be one of those things. I won't make someone from my own home kill me. I'm going to lie here until the cravings go away.
(America is going to shit, and only Joseph and the Family at Eden’s Gate are fully equipped to deal with the coming Collapse. )

Silicgel is the byproduct of <Arachnids> converting minerals they collect into a substance they excrete much like honey bees. The Silicgel is the key ingredient in the 3D manufacturing process. Without it, complex printing of items would be impossible.
A Queen controls all the <ARACHNIDS> in the local colony. Killing a Queen will cause the <ARACHNIDS> in the area to flee and unlock the location she controls.
Weapons use energy. Once empty there is a cooldown.

<Arachnids> have the ability to burrow and travel beneath the surface when they are threatened or in danger. They have successfully adapted this as a form of attack and employ it with great success.

The red part of arachnids’ back is their weakpoint. See tutorial page for more information.

It’s been two days and still no sign of Howie. He went out for some samples and never came back, and now there’s some strange howling from deep in the forest. I’m starting to worry that Eli was right and we should’ve left when we had that chance. I’ve seen more of these Eden’s Gate people driving around in their white trucks, but we stay hidden anytime they come this way. Bailey and Kent want to try and make a run for it. With the increased Cult presence I don’t know if we’d make it. Godammit, I’m a scientist, I’m not cut out for this.
Gary I’ve gathered all the gear we stripped off the prisoners and put it in the trailer office for safe keeping. Let me know when the truck is here to pick it up and I’ll unlock it for you. Chris

Eli You asked me to keep an eye on the Lumber Mill and report any unusual activity. My radio’s busted so I’ll write my findings down and deliver them to you in person. 1) I’ve seen numerous trucks offloading prisoners – usually 6 or so at a time. 2) I can hear sermons over the loudspeakers day and night. 3) They’ve got those Judges of theirs patrolling the area. I’ve also seen signs of this “Cook” you talk about. I’m going to try and get some more intel on him before I return. Harrison

They’re still after me, I know it. I was able escape when they weren’t looking, but it’s only a matter of time before they track me down. I was able to gather some supplies, but my leg hurts so much I can’t even stand on it anymore. I’m going to try and flag down some help in the morning. Wish me luck.

I had to bury Bailey today. The bite must’ve nicked an artery or something… she lost so much blood. I was with her in the end… I was there, holding her hand, and then she was gone. I know I’m not much of a soldier, but I’m not going to let their deaths be in vain. I might not be good with a gun, but I can help Eli and his Whitetails another way. I’m going to science the shit out of these… what did Eli call them? “Judges”. With the right data, I can make a difference… all these deaths won’t be for nothing.
7 Rifles 10 Pistols 2 Shotguns 12 Knives (Hunting/Pocket) 12 Wedding rings 9 Necklaces 8 Earings 14 Smartphones 10 Wallets 6 Watches 16 pairs of Shoes 15 Shirts 13 Pants 6 Skirts/Dresses
St. Graham – Age 26 F. Harrison – Age 62 (Deceased) P. Parsons – Age 21 (Deceased) J. Stiles – Age 24 M. Graham – Age 29 (Deceased) T. Fuller – Age 43

Are you tired of all those fat cats down in D.C. that do nothing but raise taxes and not much else? Well, now’s your time to give it to the man and put one of our own in power! List of Accomplishments: 1) Has zero DUI convictions 2) Has never run for Senate before 3) Kept his house, his car, and over half his assets during the divorce 4) Has never been caught cheating on his wife If you want a friend in high places, Vote Hurk Sr. for Senator!

We were attacked last night by … something. They got Kent first, dragged him away to who knows where. Bailey got bit on the leg, it looks pretty bad. We’ll try to get to a hospital in the morning. Not sure what attacked us. I’d guess it’s some sort of canis loupus, but they’ve been changed somehow. From the red markings on the forehead I’m pretty sure whatever did it that it’s man-made, but what sort of chemical/biological compound could produce such a result? I have some theories but I’ll need better samples to figure this out.

6:00 am – Wake Up. 6:30 am – Roll call. 7:00 am – Check bodies. 8:00 am – If pass checklist, escort to the pen for pick up. 9:00 am – Words of the Father. 2:00 pm – Hose down prisoners and cages. 3:00 pm – Prisoner pick-up at the main gates. 5:00 pm – Afternoon prayers – Praise the Father. 7:00 pm – Lights out.

Those fuckers have taken everything from me. My house, my wife, my family… everything. If no one is going to stand up to them then it’s up to me. If I’m going to hell I’m going to take as many as I can with me. They fucked with the wrong Marine.

These pathetic sinners are bringing us down. Jacob says we need more people in our church, but not these worthless pieces of shit. They deserve nothing but to feel the purifying heat of fires of our faith. Let their screams be our hymns as we ascend into heaven.

Eli, one of those Whitetail Militia, came by last night. He was trying to convince us to get out of Hope County, that these “Eden’s Gate” people meant us harm. I told him that our work here wasn’t finished, that it would still be a few days before we could leave. He said “for such smart folks we were acting like a bunch of idiots” and stormed off. I’m pretty sure he’s just paranoid like all the other folks in this park. I mean, who would come after a bunch of conservationists?

You so called Whitetail Militia are done for. You think you are fighting the good fight, you are only delaying the inevitable. We found you here, we can find you anywhere. Run all you want, you can’t outrun our judgement.

For me, my obsession with Bigfoot started when I was a teenager. I had a summer job as a counsellor at a nearby camp. I was in charge of looking after a bunch of 12 year-olds, take them hiking, canoeing, and generally try to keep them alive. We also went out into the woods to do some backpacking and camping out in the wilderness. I’ll never forget what I saw that night. We had set up camp deep in the woods and were just about finished our dinner when we heard something large move through the underbrush. At first we worried it could be a bear, but what we saw that night wasn’t any like any bear I’ve ever seen….

While the Canis Lupis seems to be the best candidate for augmentation, I suggest testing our formula on other species to see if we can’t get a similar result. Here is my short list of potential candidates:
1) Moose – Alces alces 2) Cougar – Puma concolor 3) Bear – Ursa Arctos Horribilis

Hey you stupid cultist fucks! You'll never get into my bunker. It's impregnable, I built it myself. But even if you do, you'll never get back out again.

If they want to access their stash again, they'll have to wait until the dog shits it back out!

Tastes like Thanksgiving turkey, if you add enough cranberry sauce.

Use the force field device to be able to sustain more damage.
Using electro grenade will paralyse enemeis alllowing you to easily kill them.
Arachnids have the ability to burrow and travel beneath the surface when they are threatened or in danger. They have successfully adapted this as a form of attack and employ it with great success.

A Queen will reveal herself once the meter is full. Killing a Queen will cause the ARACHNIDS in the area to flee and unlock the Terminal location.
This zone know has the chaos as some sort of chemicals reaction affecting gravity belt. This blocks it usage in this region of the world.
This special prototype robot can be controlled by Nick. Come back here to print another one if it dies.
Use the invisibility cloak device to avoid being detected by the arachnids
A dead Queen's heart releases strong pheromones. Dropping it in an area will attract a living Queen. This can be used to force her out whenever she's hiding during combat.

All weapons rely on [a special energy] to work. Unlike regular ammo these weapons will always regain their capacity overtime. As a rule of thumb, the more energy is consume the stronger the damage, but also the longer the cooldown time.
Shoot at the core of the launchers to destroy them.
Interacting with eggs will give you pulp. Throwing pulp on an arachnid will turns the other arachnids against it!

Disruptors were placed all around the world to protect the facilities by sending [pheromone] disrupting arachnids behaviour. Activating disruptors will make any arachnids nearby attack other arachnids.
With the power glove equipped, you can perform melee attack on arachnids. To perform a death from above attack jump on its back and press the RIGHT_THUMBSTICK when the prompt shows up.

Access Terminals to ANNE are installed throughout the facility. The terminals need to be rebooted to help ANNE restore her operations. Each of these terminals hold data related to 3D printing and access to local teleporters.

Alien creatures known as Arachnids can attack you at both close and long range. The most common arachnids have an inherent weakness in their top rear quarter aim for the red part of arachnids’ back to inflict them maximum damage!
Mars has only 38% of the gravity of Earth. So a 200 pound human only weights 76 pounds. This means an average person can jump 9 feet high on Mars!
Hey Bill That stuff you asked me to hold on to, it’s locked up in the radio room. It was the only place I thought would be safe enough. Just come find me if you need the key. - Peter

To the owner of the boat, I’m so sorry I took the "Beast Master". I really didn’t have any other choice. They’ve taken everything, it’s only a matter of time before they come for me. If I make it out of here I’ll send help. Simon

To all you so called Whitetail Militia, this is your final warning. We have been tolerant of your presence, but the Father only has so much patience for unbelievers. You can try to hide in your cabins, but we will find you. Either you join us of your own free will or you will be butchered, one by one if we have to.

It is important to follow these steps when checking if an animal is good for conversion. 1) Injuries – Check the animal for any visible open wounds or signs of distress. If the injuries are relatively minor then treat with an antiseptic and continue to step 2. If the wounds are severe or could cause infection then the animal must be destroyed. 2) Age – Select only fully grown wolves (2 years or older). If they are too young or too old then they must be destroyed. 3) Aggressiveness – Those animals that show aggressive traits seem to have a better chance to survive the conversion process. If the wolf shows no aggressive traits then they should be destroyed. Doc
PARK CLOSED Whitetail Park is closed until further notice. If you have any questions or need to report an incident please phone the local Ranger Station at 555-1212 Whitetail Park Rangers

I’m so sorry. You told me to shut the door if the cult came, even if you were still outside. I did it. God help me I did it. But I could still hear everything. You pleading, Phil screaming. Oh God the screaming. I can still hear it. I don’t want to hear it anymore.

I spotted another fucking Peggie patrol. This one is on foot so I’m going to follow them, see where they go. I dragged all our gear up to the lookout so that animals can’t get at it. Be back soon -Paul

Tanner The last two shipments of Bliss have caused a fucked up reaction with the animals. They're dying on me. If there has been a change to the chemical formula you gotta let me know. We’ve been perfecting this for weeks now, and even a minor change could screw with the results. I don’t need to tell you the importance of our work here. Doc
9:00 – 9:45 Obstacle Course 10:00 – 11:30 Endurance Run 12:30 - 1:15 – Weapons training 1:30 pm – Return to Chalet

Dylan You have to listen to me, we have to get out of here. It’s not safe anymore, not with the Father and his followers taking over the whole damn place. They got everyone running scared, and if you were smart you’d run too. I have a plan to get out of here, and I really want you to come with me, but it looks like you’ve already made up your mind. If you want to join these fuckers, I can’t stop you, but there’s no way I’m staying here. Change your goddamned mind, Dylan. Love – Skylar

God, I hate being sent here. It’s so remote no one bothers to come up this way. I can see everyone else, shooting down sinners out by the Dam and I’m stuck here looking after some supplies. Fuck it, I’m going out to shoot something, I don’t care what it is.

Our Father, my brother, has seen the end of the world, and we’re not ready. No one is ready. We have polluted our minds by letting the pathetic sycophants that run our government support those that can’t help themselves. They are our anchors, holding us back. We spend so much effort to lift them up that instead they are dragging us down. It is time we cut the chaff from the wheat, to cull the herd, once and for all.
Whitetail Park is closed until further notice. If you have any questions or need to report an incident please phone the local Ranger Station at 555-1212 Whitetail Park Rangers

Once I was lost in the wilderness and as I came to understand the wilderness, I too became wild, and out of this wilderness I was fostered anew, not just as a man, but as an animal, clothed in the blood of my kill, wild in the heart, and with a powerful hunger for all those who would trespass against me and the wilderness I now called my home.

I don’t know why the Whitetails keep fighting us, don’t they know we’re trying to save them? They came at us again today, but we were ready. We lost Jimmy and Trevor, but we killed at least 6 of them before they turned tail and ran. With the weapons and supplies up here we can hold off almost any attack they throw at us.

Okay, I’ve got it all planned out. If I see any of those Peggies heading this way, first thing I'm gonna do is throw my gear down the cliff, then I’m gonna wingsuit down. I’d like to see those Peggies try to follow me then.

Preparations are looking good, but there are still some supplies that I’m concerned about. Considering the number of people we are expecting and the length of time we’re going to be down here. Water – We have access to the lake, but we will have to make sure we have sufficient purification tablets and filtration. We should get more chlorine bleach as a back-up. Food Stores – Our grains and starches seem to be covered, but I’m worried about fruits and vegetables. Let’s see what we can do to get more canned goods so that we don’t all end up with scurvy.

I’ve seen what they do when they catch you. They do things, they change you. You’re not you anymore. I ran into Patrick, but it wasn’t him anymore. He tried to kill me! I don’t think I’m strong enough. I don’t want to be changed, I want to be me. If this is my final choice then at least I know that I’m the one making it. - Jenny
While waiting to respawn, use [Steer] to cycle between spawn points. Press [MenuButton3] to change loadouts.
You believe you're on the righteous path, you believe you're a force for good. But you're not.
I am not here to take your life. I'm here to give it to you.
You will say "Yes, I will be saved." You will say, "Yes, I will be reborn." You will say, "Yes, I will cleanse my soul for the project at Eden's Gate."
I spent my entire life looking for more things to say 'yes' to.
We must wash away our past. We must expose our sins. We must atone.
Brothers and sisters... Someone out there is not playing by the rules.
You will confess. Every sin you've ever committed, no matter how petty, no matter how small... I will pull from you.
Sin must be exposed so it may be absolved.
You will be cleansed. You will confess your sins, and you will be offered atonement.
There are only two paths left: salvation and death.
What if I told you, you could be free from sin? What if I told you that everything you ever dreamed could come true?
We're going to share a beautiful moment. And you're going to tell me your deepest, darkest fears...

I stayed at my post for a while. No action. Leaders are being paranoid, all this place needs to guard it is those bones there. (I didn't do it).
I'm heading back to the County Jail. If you're against Eden's Gate and looking for safety that's a good place to start.

A bundle of arrows. Don't waste them on a archery competition with the Sheriff of Nottingham.

Emits a smoke cloud that reduces visibility. Just like uncle Benny's farts on bean night.

Arrow that will start a fire on impact. It's straight up medieval.
Ammo for Submachine Guns. Some pepper for your steak.
An improvised explosive device found across different aisles of a hardware store.
A bottle-based incendiary. Beauty in its simplicity.
Healthcare in a box. You decide whether this is mandatory or optional.
Armor-piercing rounds for Submachine Guns. Makes armor so hole-y, you'll think it was blessed by the Pope.
This rocket releases a tight cluster of explosives. For when precision is not a priority.
Ammo for Assault Rifles. There are many like 'em, but these ones are yours.

At least you can see the damage. It's the damage we carry around on the inside that is the real problem.
The skin of a skunk. If you're concerned about the smell, just take a beer & tomato paste bath.
The skin of an alpha boar. Its fly infested head will say the beast is really inside us all. Good lord!
The skin of an alpha black bear. Now work on your Welsh accent and prepare for winter.
Well. It's well done. Add a side of ketchup and you've got yourself the favorite meal of a U.S. President.
The skin of a deer. Remember that animated movie about an orphaned deer? Yeah...
The skin of an alpha hare. They really should have taken that left turn at Albuquerque.
The skin of an alpha moose. Who knew vegetarians could get this swole?
The Father and his Heralds begin to share their message with the people of Hope, offering them salvation from the Collapse.
Joseph Seed is forced to defend his family from traitors and the unbelievers they bring to Eden's Gate.
The Seals are opened and fire cleanses the Earth. In the Gates, our Family waits.
Joseph Seed hears the Voice. It calls on him to become a leader to give hope to wayward souls.
The Father prophesies that the coming of a White Horse is the signal that the Collapse is near.
The Voice reveals the coming Collapse, and the true purpose of Joseph's ministry: to save our souls from destruction and guide them to Eden's Gate.
Joseph Seed's message reaches the ears of his first true followers. They soon begin to call him their Father because of his great wisdom and guidance.
Chaos swallows the Garden as the First Seal is broken. The heretics fight against the Family as we collect our final harvest of souls and material goods.
Joseph Seed collects his blood family--John, Jacob, and Faith. He anoints them as his Heralds so that they may help guide the growing family of believers.
Joseph Seed affirms his obedience to the Voice by cleansing himself with his own two hands, becoming born again.
The Bliss is gifted to disciples who are too full of fear and doubt, elevating them to Angels who can better help prepare for the Collapse.
The Voice guides the Father to bring his disciples to Hope, the place destined to be our New Garden after the Collapse.
After seven years, the Gates are opened to a changed world and the Father's Chosen inherit our New Garden.
Used to lure wolves into traps so that they can be converted into Judges.
These objects of worship are placed along the pilgrimage path and beyond.
Filled with a volatile mix of drugs and fertilizer.

Karen & Benny, John's scared us. We're taking whatever we can find at the dock and we're leaving. There's money on the table to cover next month’s rent. When things get back to normal, we'll come back. Promise. Please stay safe, --The Haglunts

Hey Karen The cult has us really scared but we're still not sure about what we're gonna do. The Haglunts wanna run, but we feel bad ditching everyone in a time of crisis. Mr. Hausercatt wants to stay and fight, but we're not fighters. We don't wanna die. After mass, we’re going to ask Pastor Jerome for advice. He always seems to know what to do with these Eden's Gate types. --Elliott & Danielle & Sammy

Ryan, If you're reading this, then you followed mommy's plan just like we practiced. That's my boy! Now take these supplies and head for the woods, and remember, if mommy doesn't show up after three hours, head South and don't look back. And don't forget to switch the safety on the gun to OFF. Very important. Love you to pieces, Mom

To All Tenants, We understand that John's reached out to some of you, in a possibly threatening manner, but that don't change the fact RENT STILL NEEDS TO BE PAID. It's not the first time the Peggies have made threats against us. Nothing bad has ever happened and nothing bad ever will. --Karen & Benny aka The Management

Doug, Don't delete the answering machine message. This is turning big. I know what I said before, but I changed my mind. They're not going to make us another offer. Maybe it's better to be safe than sorry. We can always come back if we were wrong. Let's take it and go, please. --Deb
Crash site of the doomed Air Cavalry helicopter.
Note to all pickers: The bears are back this year. Remember the rules: 1. Pick with a buddy. 2. Clean up any food & trash Stay safe, everybody! --Doug & Debbie
A small livestock farm, taken over by VC.

Russell, Please read this. Eden's Gate has been hounding me for our land ever since you left. Then, the other day, some of them came to the house and told us we've been marked. They said that Ryan was gonna get taken into their Project and that Boomer was gonna be given to a fella named Jacob up North. Look, I know we've had our differences, but you've left me to be the only one looking out for our boy, and I've decided that I'm standing my ground. There's no way I'm letting these bastards break up our family. Whatever happens, I hope you understand. Rae-Rae
An overgrown and abandoned family home.

Hey everybody, This is a bumper crop! I've never seen so many apples. Ten years worth of blood, sweat, and tears has led us to this. We're talkin' record profits. Let's pick 'em quick, ship 'em out, then we'll have a party with all the cider you can drink, on us. Things are finally going right for Gardenview! --Doug & Debbie

Karen & Benny, FUCK JOHN SEED! That maniac can't intimidate me. Anyone who wants to help me defend this flophouse just needs to check the shed or under the boxes out back. You'll get what you need. With love, Mr. Hausercatt
Doug, I'm leaving you this note to remind you: DO NOT LEAVE THE OFFICE KEY IN THE MARKET STALL. They want this place, let's not make it easier for them. --Deb

I don't even know if they bothered looking. They just saw the missing gear, turned on their heels, came for my family. And hung them here. So I had to pass each and every one of them as they rot in order to get at what I stole.

Let it be known that you have been judged and found guilty in the eyes of the Father. You have continued to supply our enemies with food and supplies from your restaurant even after we have warned you not to. You can expect the full wrath of Eden’s Gate to fall upon you, your family, and everything you own. The fire will cleanse your soul.
Mad ramblings on a crumpled piece of paper

I know you warned us, but now it's too late. We thought we could handle it, but we had no idea the resources that Jacob would bring to bear. But we will not give up. This is our land, by God, and no one, not the Government, the army and sure as hell not some religious nutcase is going to drive us off. If nothing else we’ll take as many of them with us as we can. Ryan Elliot

I’ve got this place locked up tighter than a frog’s ass. There’s no way those damn Peggie’s can find me here. There’s lots of food, but I saw some mushrooms that look edible, I should be able to supplement my diet with those if I have to.

THey caN try, bUt they wOn’t SUCCEED. I haVe sEEn them, the AliEns. TheY cOMe FRom the sHAdoWs to EAT our SKIN. THEy cAn’t HaVE iT. I Will eAt it FirST.

I hope Travis doesn’t get in trouble. I saw him sneak out last night to meet up with his new friends. He keeps talking about this “Father” guy, and how special he is, and how much he needs us. I’ll tell the camp counselor in the morning if he’s not back by then.

We found Cheeseburger as a young cub in the dumpster behind a local restaurant. He was an orphan, his mother shot by poachers and left for dead. He was brought to the FANG Center where he was bottle fed and nurtured back to health. While he is kept to a strict diet of berries and fish, from time to time we’ll sneak him his favorite snack: cheeseburgers. Now because of his emotional attachment to humans he could never be released back into the wild. Instead, he has become one of the most beloved residents of the Center.
Writing on a lined piece of paper

Chad Wolanski is guilty of giving aid to Eli and his sinful Whitetails by supplying them food and shelter. Let this be a warning for all those that would stand against the Father. We will come for you, your house, your business, your family. There are only two sides: you are either with the Father, or against him.
Pray you choose the right side.
Writing on a crumpled piece of paper

They can have my food, over MY DEAD BODY! I’ll fucking shoot anybody that tries to take it. This all belongs to ME! They tried to get me the other day but a few grenades showed 'em I meant business! Gonna celebrate with some more mushroom stew.

There has been numerous reports of disturbances within the Park, many of them appear to involve members of the church that goes by the name of Eden’s Gate. Some of these altercations have resulted in injuries, some of them quite serious. When patrolling the park keep an eye out for anything unusual and report any more incidents. We don’t want this situation to escalate out of control. Montana Park Rangers
We regret to inform you that Old Sun Outfitters will be closed for the foreseeable future. The atmosphere in this county has become so toxic that it is no longer safe for me and my family to stay.
Skunk - 10:00 am Wolves - 11:00 am Cougar - 1:00 pm Cheeseburger – 12:00 pm and 6:00 pm Wolverine – 2:00 pm Eagles – 3:00 pm

We regret to say that the Breakthrough Camp is closing its doors. For us, teaching the next generation our ways and the ways of the forest was our passion, but due to circumstances beyond our control we simply can’t continue to put these children at risk. While we have always called the Whitetail Mountains our home, recent events have made it impossible to guarantee the safety of the children in our care. We hope to return one day, but until then: Giga-waabamin menawaa
There’s no way those fuckers are going to get me up here. I’ve got everything I need here, and there’s no way up here without a rope. If they try they’re going to get a mouth full of lead.

As requested, loud speakers have been placed in strategic locations and will play messages sent from Combat Intelligence Office. Radio surveillance of selected channels is ongoing. A listening watch on all other frequencies will be maintained around the clock.

FRAGO P-44 MACV SAIGON SUPERCEDES OPORD P-43 INITIAL OBJECTIVES/OPERATING ORDER P-43 CHANGED. LATEST AERIAL RECON SHOWS NEW 100mm AA GUN EMPLACEMENTS LOCATED EAST OF YOUR POSITION. MISSION OBJECTIVE CHANGED TO SUPPRESSION AND DESTRUCTION OF THOSE GUNS. EXPECT MIXED BATTALION SIZED OPPOSITION THROUGHOUT AO. EXTRACTION POINT AND TIME REMAINS UNCHANGED

RADIO DISPATCH 44-25 MUST BE TRANSMITTED ENCODED Subject: DISPOSITION OF FORCES Air Defense positions in this sector have been established as ordered. 100mm AA emplacements are dug in and fully operational. Loud speakers for broadcast of patriotic messages have been installed and are operating 24/7.

AFTER ACTION REPORT 10-22 1500hours Engaged fast ground attack aircraft in sector. One aircraft was hit and destroyed. Two chutes were observed to the west and southwest of this position. The chute to the SW has come down across the river. Have sent patrols to find and capture enemy airmen. Will send follow up report when pilots are located.

Something is killing all the trees and crops, everything is dying. We are using flamethrowers to clear the dead vegetation. This situation is impacting the local supplies of food and there are growing concerns that the water is contaminated.

COMMANDER, SECTOR E5 You are to select three worthy candidates from your ranks to attend Foreign Language Training. These individuals must be transferred from your command effective immediately. They will proceed to Regional Headquarters via fastest available transport. Forward names and ranks of selected individuals by 0900 tomorrow.

Order of battle as follows. Ground forces will attack enemy firebase at 0600. First objective, take control of large gun emplacement to the west of firebase. We will suppress air attacks with AA until ground forces can close with enemy. It is imperative to close with enemy as quickly as possible to nullify their air support. Grab them by the belt!

AFTER ACTION REPORT 10-2 1400 hours Eight aircraft were visually confirmed and fired upon while transiting this sector. One jet was destroyed, it is believed to have crashed SSE of this station. Two parachutes were reported by spotters, one directly south of this location, the other southeast. A search is ongoing.

After capturing this gun, we have operated in support of our ground forces attacking the enemy firebase. Additionally we claim one enemy aircraft. Pilots were seen ejecting, parachutes came down due west and due south of this gun-the chute to the south may have drifted to the other side of the river. Unable to conduct a search due to ongoing combat operations.

Due to increased enemy air activity, we have moved all Command and Control functions into the Plantation Bunker. If attacked, my staff and I will shelter in the bunker until the all clear is given. Appropriate supplies and special weapons have been relocated there until further notice. Daily inspection notes to follow.

We are sorry to inform you that your brother has been killed. Stop. His unit was heavily engaged in the area surrounding Quang Tri where he was killed on the second day of fighting. Stop. Heavy rain and continued enemy bombardment made it impossible to recover his body. Stop. The sympathy and support of the Party is with you! Stop.

Attention: All Principal Agents! Infiltrators are moving with impunity through this region. They disguise themselves as local farmers and fisherman. You must be vigilant! Follow procedure! If an individual cannot be properly identified, hold for further questioning from the Sector Field Intelligence Officer! Broadcast this warning on the loud speakers in your sector!

Placement of Patriotic loud speakers has been completed on schedule. Intercepted enemy radio transmissions have been transcribed and forwarded to Combat Intelligence Office. Will continue to monitor radio traffic coming in and out of enemy Firebase Echo.

Shot down ground attack fighter. Both pilots ejected and came down to the NNE and SE. Search parties are looking, have not checked in yet. REQUIRED SUPPLIES 100mm Frag-HE rounds X400 7.62mm X3000 Fire control… miscellaneous parts, list to follow Camouflage netting 20 by 20 meter

Rock Bass seek moderately warm water, so if you're looking for some, just pee in a lake.
Its habitat has been described as “clean, complex and connected” which, admit it, is also what you put on your last online dating profile.
Pallid Sturgeon live over sand and gravel, in strong currents, because life is pain.
This hard-fighting game fish prefers natural cover but can adapt to various environments which means they're probably better at video games than you.
Kokanee spawn over sand, gravel, and loose rubble in lower portions of tributary streams. Those sexy, sexy tributary streams.
Smallmouth Bass feed on almost any available item, from zooplankton to frogs because they are always really high.
Largemouth Bass are aggressive and opportunistic feeders, making them the freelance writers of the aquatic kingdom.
Arctic Grayling Salmon do not coexist well with other fishes, because they're bad motherfuckers who don't take shit from nobody.
Chinook Salmon are supposed to move from fresh water to the ocean, but today's younger generations say the ocean's rent is too expensive.
These fish occupy only high altitude fresh water lakes and rivers, usually in mountain areas that are highly inaccessible. They are the doomsday preppers of the fish world.
SPOILER ALERT: Lake Trout live in lakes.

Note Placeholder Title for the Note 2 of D3_MEGA_01
Note Placeholder Description for the Note 3 of D3_MEGA_01

After spending so long in a literal prison, you'd think American life would feel...different. Land of the FREE and all that. I got back here and some religious nut was midway through buying my house out from under me. And I fought for that. I fought for some "John Seed" jackass to have the "freedom" to legally take my shit from me just because some money's changing hands. You can bet I'll never see a dime. Only thing I brought back from 'Nam was a goddamned lighter. Can't stand the sight of it. Maybe it can do one last thing for me though. Before I go.
We have to take control of this place. but there's a heathen with a sniper rifle making our lives hell. Watch yourselves.

You know about John Seed's bunker right? No? It’s a sex dungeon for the ultra elite familiars. The richest humans in the world come there to have sexual rituals in coffins filled with blood in hopes that one of these interdemional demon goblins might posses their body. They call it the enlightenment. Those selected become the true ruling class. The 1% of the 1%. The illuminati. I’ve seen videos of the rituals. Disgusting.

The Bliss is flourishing in the East. It's time to introduce it in the Valley. We're getting regular shipments via the River, and we've appropriated silos across the region to store our special fertilizer. Take care when filling the silos, you know how sensitive the Bliss can be to heat. Joseph's going to be so proud of us.

Dmitri - You've got the only hard copy of the tape that exists in the world. We're hiding you in plain sight in America. We've found a little religious extremist group in the northwest. They're armed but small time. Should be the perfect cover to shake that CIA assassin on your tail. Lay low until we contact you. - G. Voronina

A man has been spotted sneaking around the perimeter of the stockyard. I've detailed his appearance to John, who's identified him as Zip Kupka. John believes he may have been employed here once. He's a lost soul and a difficult one at that. Very unpredictable. We need to be on high alert around this man as he may try to compromise our operation.

If you are reading this, then we are already gone. Woodson's Pig Farm is officially closed. This is a decision we deeply regret, but to be frank, John Seed's encroachments onto our territory along with his threats have left us with no other choice. For generations, we have proudly served the people of this great county, and we sincerely thank you for supporting our business over the years. But, at the end of the day, the safety of our family comes first.
With love, The Woodsons
Stay away from the cult's "Angels." They're fast and deadly and they don't die easy. Having said that, a bullet to the head can do the trick.

Casey: Everything you need for the Testy Festy is in the barn. Decorations, lockboxes, the whole deal. Stashed it there for ya not too long ago. It's one of them things, you know? Things go to shit, but nothin' keeps you sane like a deep fried testicle festival. Like in times of war, you still celebrate Christmas, that kind of thing. Well this is our Christmas. Testicle Christmas. Kenny

Brett, For all the shit that spews out of Zip's mouth, he was right this time. I couldn't sleep tonight so I went out for a walk. Passed by the stockyard and heard the animals making weird noises just like Zip said. So, I snuck in. Dude...there's these weird looking barrels everywhere. Stuff stinks. Checked some of the pens and it looks like the water and feed are tainted with this stuff. Just what the hell are the night shift guys doing here? We need to talk to someone about this. ASAP. Aaron
We will cull the herd. We will do what needs to be done.
We know what happens to the weak.
I cull the herd. It's what I do.
Now, the collapse is upon us, and this time the lives of the few outweigh the lives of the many.
Give yourself over to the father. Make your sacrifice... And the judges will deem you worthy.
You are in crisis. Don't fight it. Give in to that.
The weak have their purpose. You'll understand that soon enough.
Humanity is once again in crisis.
Our time is near. This is no accident. This is no surprise. We have been warned throughout history.
My soldiers are strong. They kill for me. They die for me.
Did you think you were free?
We have forgotten what it is to be strong.
Invert the pitch direction when looking up and down in flying vehicles.
Invert the look direction when looking up and down.

Team update: All bets are on batch 9, the hybrid of last year's 6 and 14. Early tests show increased peace, lower risk of agitation. Dr. Feeney's tests will confirm soon. We've improved on the original plant so much, so quickly. Faith gives us a better bliss each season. Keep her in your prayers. Without her none of this exists. Without her we die in terror.

{This mattress is infested with bed bugs, just like Eden's Gate has infested Hope with their delusions, their atrocities. Everyone turns a blind eye until we bleed, until the marks on our skin show. But it's too late. They multiple and they grow. They're immune to laws and to boundaries. They will find you. They will hunt you. There's no stopping a pest after blood and they will spill it all to punish bearers of deadly sins. We will never sleep.

Way back when, this moose went all nutty and started running headlong as fast as it could towards a moving train. Guess the conductor wasn't in the mood for mooseberry jam but he has no idea what to do. This moose is sprinting it's massive lumpy body towards a moving train. For no reason. Nothing's chasing it. It's just running because something misfired in its big brain. So I'm about to see some carnage I did not sign up for when the conductor pulls the train's whistle. It's just loud and sudden enough for the moose to toss its head and start sprinting back into the woods. I've been running headlong into a moving train called Eden's Gate and it's time I get out while I still can.

A cult doesn't look like a cult when you sign up that's the whole point. Remember that when you say I brought this on myself. I signed up, sure, but I changed my mind and changing my mind is my god-given American right. If they want to hunt me down they can try. They can fucking try.
Placeholder description for Note 3 for D7_MEGA_01

Notice anything funny when you're out in the woods? No baby animals. The Bliss has turned all animals homosexual. Dogs, cats, woodland creatures, and farm animals alike. Even the god damn frogs. None of them are reproducing anymore and it's havin' all kinds of side effects. Wolves are attacking humans. Steers are becoming super aggro, and the frogs….the frogs are having massive orgies. And before you got bent out of shape. I’ve got no problem with homosexuals. My brother is a homo. He’s a great man with a wonderful family. There is nothing wrong with homosexuality, but there is something wrong with pumpin’ chemicals into the air that turns ALL animals gay. It’s unnatural. I can’t go to the swimming hole anymore because it’s a god damn gay bathhouse for frogs. These peggie demons must be stopped.

Bliss is allocated to certain places for a REASON. It's vital we keep the Bliss we need for after the Collapse separate from the Bliss we're using for Angels and the water supply. If someone comes round asking for a few spare barrels, always get word from Faith first. And keep an eye on whoever's asking.
Placeholder title for Note 3 for D7_MEGA_01

Samples 7, 9, and 12 from this week are ready for Dr. Feeney's analysis. Watch the dates on the labels so we won't have a repeat of last week. Tidy the workspace before he comes. His expertise makes him irreplaceable. His standards are fair so we need to meet them.

Came here on a starlit night to leave this world as I entered it: alone. Things are ending and I don't want to be around to see that. Appreciate the beauty of this world, and the people in it, while you can.

The more potent the flower, the brighter the Bliss. At Faith's word, I've been propagating a new breed of flowers that'll speed the Angel-making process up like nobody's business. Protect these flowers well.
Praise Faith, Praise the Father.
