The owner here died as they lived: burning with the passionate desire to protect their land. We can tell John we made it so.

I found the Resistance mark on the wall, so I know these sinners were hiding something to take up arms against us. Search the entire cider factory top to bottom until you find it. Smash everything you can until you find it.
Day two. The water tower was a bust. I've spent too long watching them pick metal and praise the Father already. Tomorrow I'm gonna pick them off, one by one. Fuck it.

PATIENT: KIMIKO RYE Weight: 159 lbs. Blood Pressure: 140/90 mmHg (HIGH) Fetus Measurement: 28cm Fetus Heart rate:150 bpm Urine Sample Provided Pelvic Exam: Cervix dilation normal Notes: Patient is feeling added stress from Eden's Gate's recent actions. Her husband's stress level with the same issue seems to be impacting her. Recommended meditation and breathing exercises.
Everything's all set up at the tower. It's a long way up, but a quick ride down. When the shit hits the fan, we'll ride right by it. ;)

I'm writing this out and keeping it close so I don't forget. Maybe it's also a purging. I know they don't like it when we talk about doubt. But things were so quiet until now. I don't see why we should be stealing and killing when we've been working hard and honestly up until now. I don't know if I'm more scared of Joseph being wrong or right at this point. I hate watching my brothers and sisters fight. I thought Eden's Gate was better than this.

PATIENT: ZIP KUPKA Affliction(s): Blockage caused by foreign objects. Treatment: Removal of foreign objects from lower body cavity Notes: Foreign Object #1: small rolled American flag Foreign Object #2: small "Lady Liberty" statue of liberty action figure (Limited Edition) Foreign Object #3: small rolled copy of the U.S. Constitution All items were removed and returned to Mr. Kupka. Health Insurance Approved Treatment? No Patient will be billed.

I can't carry around the guilt anymore. For years I just put it in a box in the back of my heart but it ate away at everything. It changed me. I need to confess. I need to be heard and...forgiven and absolved. But I also can't go to prison. I can't I can't I can't I won't I'll die there. This John Seed man said all I'd have to do is say yes. I could confess, and have this weight off me, and never have to be behind bars. I'm seeing him tomorrow then. God, I can't wait.

The uncreative person classifies something as “junk” when they can no longer see a use for it. A person possessing a creative mind will never draw the line between useful item and junk item.
Things are useFULL, not useLESS!
The concept of things being disposable is the only thing manufactured in our world. It was created by capitalists and corporations!
EVERYTHING CAN BE USED TO CREATE SOMETHING ELSE!

Day one. The sightlines from the billboard and the power plant aren't as good as I wanted. The peggies moved into the railyard. They must want the metal. I'll scout the water tower tomorrow just to be sure I've counted them all, then it's go time. Fucking tired of their hymns.

PATIENT: MARY MAY FAIRGRAVE Affliction(s): Bumps, nodules, irritations, and swelling of the skin. Persistent allergic reaction and infection of the skin caused by a tattoo. Traces of cobalt, chromium, and cadmium found in ink. Patient is allergic to all three. Recommended Treatment: Non-Cosmetic Tattoo Removal Notes: Cortisone injections have been administered for temporary pain relieve. The tattoo was forcefully administered. Consistent with other Eden's Gate tattoos. Health Insurance Approved Treatment? Yes Patient will not be billed.
Say YES or what happened to the Stricklands will happen to YOU.

Living without worldly possessions ain't what it's cracked up to be I ain't achieved enlightenment once. Not once! Honestly, it's getting cold again and I don't think I can survive another Montana winter without a roof over my head. Them Eden's Gate folks have come by twice now and I can't help but think it's time to just take the free food, clothing, and roof. All I gotta do is smile and nod through the winter, then I'll just move on down the road. Easy peasy.

I've seen too many of our brothers and sisters fall off and injure themselves on those wires. Nobody has the hand strength to hang on for so long! It's too dangerous. I think it's a trap the "resistance" made.
I've scouted this place out long enough. Cult's up to no good. Can't wait for backup, I'm gonna attack.

The techs seem excited about a new strain. I'll be at the Conservatory soon to confirm. Might finally be the one I give my name to. We'll have to celebrate privately rather than in the spotlight of academic publishing I suppose. I also want to celebrate winning our bet. I'll find some good whisky. Keep the bunk warm. --Feeney
Don't let them get into your head. Resist with everything you have. We have eyes on the pilgrimage and we'll get you out. Stay strong. -The Cougars
Placeholder description for note 2 for E7_MEGA_01

{Herald Faith, The final pilgrimage route has been chosen. We did a test run with a volunteer. Before she lost lucidity she was able to tell us everything we needed to know. Consider the matters of the pacing and strength of bliss in the water settled. It's our honor to tell you we are ready to install the waystations when the Collapse is near. Your next angels will be the happiest and strongest.
Placeholder title for note 3 for E7_MEGA_01
Placeholder description for note 3 for E7_MEGA_01

{To my guardians, Because we have each other, we are already strong. But when the Collapse comes, this gate will need to be the heart of our strength. Guard it with your lives, knowing that any sacrifice you make will be for the future of humanity's greatest ideals and dreams. Jacob and Joseph have chosen you to guard this gate. You should be very proud. I know you serve me with love, but never forget that this will be your home, too. If you falter from this purpose, remember the bliss is there for you. With love, Faith

Powdered Bliss is only made by Faith's private chemists in her Gate. Liquid Bliss has a better Resurrection rate for the Angels saturated with it. Sure, the powdered stuff is more powerful, but you knock a body down on that stuff it's not getting up. Angels need LIQUID Bliss because only liquid can reliably get them back on their feet.
Trust in Faith, trust in the Angels.
Placeholder title for note 2 for E7_MEGA_01

{Reminders for new initiates working with angels: They cannot understand complex instructions. Keep it simple. Don't act aggressive near them, they get agitated easily. Supervise them near open flames or other dangerous equipment. They don't need much sleep, food, or drink, so let them work. They love the Father's voice and our music, so play both for them often. When they cry in the fields it's because they're happy. Don't worry. Anyone caught mistreating an angel will be severely punished by the Herald Faith herself.

A legendary stuntman who left this world the way he entered it: Face first onto a pile of rocks.
The Baptist in the West. The youngest of the Seed brothers, John is in charge of reaping the land of supplies that will help the Project survive.
He made it through Nam with his buddies. Now he’s an old man, his buddies are gone, and this is not the America he fought for in his youth.
A wanted arsonist, Charlemange Victor Boshaw IV hides out where he can live his fire-blazing, rockstar fantasies.
A member of Eli's Whitetail Militia.
The tough-as-nails barkeep who blames Eden's Gate for the death of her parents.
A self-proclaimed conspiracy "realist" who finds a new reason to hate the government with each passing day.
A bonafide prepper and the leader of the Whitetail Militia. He helped Eden's Gate design their survival bunkers before he wised up.
The Siren in the East. The youngest in the Seed family pacifies unruly followers to make way for the Collapse. Some believe she's only an illusion.
The Father. The middle Seed brother heard a Voice that told him to initiate a great Project, to prepare for the Collapse of everything. And so he has.
A world traveler who chose Hope County to put down roots, and those roots are on the way - she's in her third trimester.
A veterinarian drafted into service as a medic. There's no one else to do it, and aren't we all animals?
A medal-winning shooter and army sniper with a vendetta against Eden’s Gate.
The long-time pet of Miss Mable. Probably named for the color of her fur and not the sweet disposition she lacks.
One of your fellow Hope County Deputies who’s a good cop when his ego doesn't get in the way.
His wit and intellect may have been blunted by paint huffing, but that hasn't stopped him from living a life of adventure.
Wilhelmina Maybelline, big cat whisperer and taxidermist. The well-being of Peaches the cougar is her top priority.
Wade Fowler's brother, he runs the business end of the F.A.N.G. Center.
She gave up city life, opened a fishing store, and began the hunt for her family’s missing legendary whiskey.
One of your fellow Hope County Deputies who has absolutely no time for bullshit and has the fists to back herself up.
The best dang pilot in Hope County. Give him a chance and he'll put on a show.
Left California for Hope County to detox from the city life. Ended up finding "modeling" gigs at the Drubman Marina, and a cult cramping his style.
A bright kid of Blackfoot heritage and the go-to person for all things computers and arcade machines. He keeps it on the down low.
The devoted sheriff of Hope County. He believes delivering justice with a gun should be a last resort. On the eve of his retirement, duty calls.
Once a homemaker, now the chief interrogator for the Whitetail Militia. They say her marshmallow blondies are to die for.
The smart-ass quartermaster for the Whitetail Militia who also has a radio broadcast to counter the Father's propaganda.
Orphaned as a cub and raised by Wade Fowler, he's the star attraction at the F.A.N.G. Center. He loves eating cheeseburgers.
An old prepper who'd worked himself to the bone and lost everything even before Eden's Gate came to town. Same shit, different horse.
Dutch’s niece. Jess is a loner who nearly lost her life in Jacob's camps, only to discover a new talent in the process: killing Peggies.
A local prepper. Merle could talk your ears off about his dream bunker, or the shelf life of canned goods.
A retired oil baron who is the undisputed master of his domain... what's left of it after the divorce.
A genius movie director envisioning a masterpiece of anarchy and gold statue wins. Even an auteur needs help to make movie magic.
Genius or crackpot? Science will decide.
A confident go-getter with deep pockets to do whatever she wants, like living with booze, bazookas, and boy toy Xander Flynn.
A lone biologist determined to unravel the mysteries of how Jacob's Judge wolves are created.

The flowers have taken to the Henbane River well. Acres and acres of land are now flush with our special crops. It's time for us to expand our gardens into the Holland Valley. With hard work, and the grace of God, we'll turn the whole county into an ocean of Bliss. And then no living creature need ever know fear again. It's a lofty dream, but the Father believes in you. If you are here with me now or if you within the sound of my voice I wish for you to stop for a moment. Look at your hands, for they born of divine design. They are a wondrous gift, allowing each of us to manufacture wonders. With these tools humanity has built wonders of technology, unparalleled civilizations, and even reached for the stars. We have shaped the earth and propelled ourselves forward. But I ask you: Is that movement the same as progress? Have we fed the earth? Have we ended slavery? Do we have equality? Do we have law? We’ve taken our gifts, our hands, and we make them into fists, and with these fists we make war. We were not given the gifts of finger and thumb to press buttons on a phone or manipulate a game controllers. To pull triggers. We were given them to clasp one another in times of turmoil, to hold and to comfort.
I AM YOUR FATHER. YOU ARE MY CHILDREN AND TOGETHER WE WILL MARCH TO EDEN’S GATE.

Greed is a kind of entitlement that will lead to taking resources destined for the project, undermining it and endangering others. Eden’s Gate houses should be spartan. Stockpiled items are communal rather than private, and only very few ‘keepsake’ type items might be found, hidden. Food is for survival, not a luxury.

Emmet Reaves had Vices and it is fair to say his biggest Vice was Gold. spent a lot of it on various rails and ironically named towns, but he did have a fortune squirreled away. never took it myself because money is the cause of literally all our pain, vices, and stresses in the U-S of A. but if you're visiting the water mill like I did, You Know The Old Saying: There's Always Something Behind A Waterfall.

I just wanted to be special. When Joseph came into my life, I felt like you'd given me a true gift, Lord. That a man who talks to you would bring me in on your holy conversation..? And so I took the name that you gave me, Lord, through Joseph: "Faith". And I am a woman made anew. But now, I'm ashamed to say, even though I carry this name, my devotion to the Project is...plagued. By Doubt. What do I do? I know you will forgive me, dear Lord. I don't know if Joseph will.

Those who put their hands upon our ark, those who mean to drown us in the flood, those who want to cast aside after all our toil -- they will find any hand they put upon us will be severed and taken from their arm. Cut from them just as easily as the farmer, after all his labor, now bends to reap his wheat.

Brothers and sisters, Now that we've occupied this garage we must immediately turn our attention toward our defenses. Half of us will bolster our convoys while the other half will begin work on The Revelator. This specialized truck will serve as a powerful deterrent to those who oppose The Father. If we're to have any chance of protecting the devoted from the Resistance, we need to get The Revelator on the road as quickly as possible.

The following is important to remember when selecting souls to be saved:
CLEAN SOULS This is a must. If a soul is tainted by this corrupt world, look into the person's eyes, see if that soul can be redeemed. Each soul must go through the cleansing before being brought to the bunker.
CLEAR MINDS We need people with intelligence, skills, and talents. Most of all, they must show they can dedicate themselves to building a better world.
ABLE BODIES Take the healthy. Take the strong. Take the young. Today’s children will be tomorrow's mothers and fathers.

It is a well known fact that bovines are the most erotic animal on God's green Earth. Sometimes I sneak out here so I can watch the bulls have sex with the cows. Please don't tell my father.

Heads up, fellas. Folks from Eden's Gate are getting pushy with our business. Rude, too. First, they want more scrap metal than we can provide. Now, they wanna buy the place outright. Sam says the vehicles they rolled up in were beefed up - reinforced with our parts! Why are they armor plating their vehicles? There's just too many questions here, boys. Next time they come by, show them the door. Our business with Eden's Gate is officially over.

The FIVE step process: 1. Unload supplies in this drop off zone. 2. Categorize and add supplies to crates. 3. Stack crates and load them into the elevator, no more than twelve at a time. 4. Send crates to lower levels where they will be divided and stored accordingly. 5. Ensure reaping vehicle is empty and fueled for the next run.

Here hangs a sinner by the name of ALEX. He and his friends came to Hope County with the idea to expose us. Despite this, the Father forgave him, and chose to save him. How did Alex repay this kindness? By a misguided attempt to free other devoted and lead them through this tunnel. John's wrath was swift, and the Chosen brought this tunnel down around them. Let this be a lesson for you all. Don't be like Alex.

Every goddamned day this ugly step-cousin of the Hollywood sign looms over my fucking shoulder. I was never one to go overboard with firearms but for the love of Pete I saved up my dollars and got me an honest-to-god RPG to take that sucker down. And I’ll give it a smile as it’s burning and whisper “No.”

For a moment, our blessed flags covered all land here. We filled this pocket of the world with the truth and justice. We put an end to the falsehood and tyranny of oppressive fools. This coalition of ignorant souls who despise us so will not stop. Even as The Collapse grows closer, the nonbelievers will come. They will slay the innocent ones among us to stop what we are doing. BE OUR SHIELD! Do everything to protect us from them.
Placeholder title for note 4 for E1_HERO_01

Les, baby, I don't know what those idiots from Hilgard Electric were so uptight about. You don't need a "degree" in "electrical engineering" or anything else. You an' me built this bunker with our bare hands. Safety hazard my entire ass. Didn't I get a smoke detector and a sprinkler system from Red's place last month? We're gonna be fine down here.

Tom,
We’re about to be overrun out here. If this finds it’s way to you, what’s left of us are holed up in the cliffside cave. They came at us at first light with everything they had, we didn’t stand a chance. The boys fought well, but there’s just too many of the bastards. Tell Joan I was thinking of her. Good luck brother,
Shaky

William,
Glad to hear you’re okay. Sure is a different type of war. We never had helicopters to fly us around, we had to march. Just remember what I taught you. Especially about shooting – if you mess up you can get yourself or your buddies killed. I had to laugh when I heard they called you “Yokel”. That was my nickname in Korea. Anyway, that’s it for now.
Yr. Dad
THE LAST WILL OF PRIVATE CHAVEZ

It’s been a while since I’ve written. Things are so busy around here with you gone. Isn’t this a great picture of the kids? North-South-East-West
If you swim in that direction, you'll find a barrel of whisky underwater. I'll pay you a good finder's fee if you find them all.

I know you think I’m crazy. Most people do, but I’m not. I’m not one of these crazy conspiracy theory guys screamin’ about big foots, flat earth, and fake moon landings. I’m not some sad lonely guy who lives such a boring life he needs to make up a fantastical reality. I don’t deal in conspiracy theory, I deal in conspiracy fact. Everything I say is the gods to honest truth. With actual evidence to support it. Which is why when I say, Eden’s Gate is a plot of a globalist cabal of demonic interdimensional goblin vampires to erode the belief in Christianity and God to usher in the apocalypse. You know it’s the truth.

Dear Mr. McDevitt,
We've received complaints that your Misty River Gas location--a subsidiary of Golden Valley Gas--has been seen with a mounted machine gun on the roof.
It's damaging our corporate identity and our reputation as the leading oil company in Montana.
Please remove all mounted weapons at your location immediately. Failure to do so will result in the revocation of your license as a franchise owner.
Regards, Laurie-Anne Finney Representative of Golden Valley Gas
We'll send these dogs to Jacob up north and he'll whip 'em into shape. Or turn 'em into food for the Judges.

My bunker's useless. I have no choice, I gotta make a run for it. I've heard rumors that someone's started a kind of militia in the mountains up north. Maybe I'll head that way. If you're readin' this, and you can find your way into my stash, help yourself.

Hey Mike,
Knew you'd come after me. You're picking the wrong side, buddy.
I miss being a SAR as much as you do but Joseph is the wrong person to take orders from. There's a group up north, supposed to be real skilled. They could use trained people like me. And like you.
Don't make this into some Fox and the Hound bullshit. If I see you wearing their colors I WILL shoot. But I'm hoping you'll wise up before then.
I miss you, man.
--Jay

Use the Flatten tool to create a flat terrain surface from the starting point, often suitable for gameplay areas.
Set the Speed parameter to control the speed at which the terrain will be flattened out.

Use the Water Layers tool to create a water plane of a given material within a sector of 64x64 meters. With careful usage of this tool, you can create a map with different water levels, also useful for placing waterfalls.

Use the Noise tool to break up the smoothness of the terrain in random natural patterns.
The Noise tool can be very useful to create mountains, after which you can apply Erosion.
Set the Speed parameter to control the speed at which modification occurs.
Set the Roughness parameter to control the size of the random natural patterns. A high value creates many small bumps and a small value creates larger bumps and smoother terrain.

Use the Raise or Lower tool to increase or decrease the terrain with a fixed height increment that will remain constant as long as you keep painting.
Set the Height parameter to adjust the height increment.

Use the Map Limits tool to define the boundaries of the playable area in the map.
Players who cross the map limits must return to battle before the countdown ends. Players who do not return to battle before the countdown ends will die.

Use the Set to Height tool to uniformly modify the terrain to a desired height, either by setting a numeric height or taking the height from an existing terrain.
Set the Speed parameter to control the speed at which the terrain will flatten.

Use the Paint Texture tool to give a different look to the terrain like grass, dirt or rock.
Assign a texture to an empty slot and then paint the chosen texture with the cursor.
You can also change the type of texture of a given slot at any time, allowing you to experiment with different looks.
Set the Minimum and Maximum Slope parameters to control the angle of the terrain slope, in degrees, on which the texture will be applied. This can be useful for only painting the sharp angles of a hill or mountain with rock. Set the minimum or maximum altitude to restrict the brush to painting only the tops of mountains or the depths of valleys.

Use the Road tool to draw a road path on the terrain. Control the points on the road to modify the path of the road.
Assign a road texture to an empty slot and then paint the road path in your map.
Set the Width parameter to adjust the width of the road.

Use the Add Vegetation tool to quickly apply vegetation to an area of the map.
Assign a type of vegetation to an empty slot and then paint the chosen vegetation with the cursor.
You can also change the type of vegetation of a given slot at any time, allowing you to experiment with different themes.

Use the Snap tool to move one or more objects so they match correctly with another object.
The Snap tool works well with objects that naturally link together like fences, bridges or blocks.

Use the Add tool to place new objects, new gameplay objects, new AI and new animation points in the map at the location of the cursor.
You can navigate through the different categories of objects by either using the drop down list, or by double-clicking on the folders.
You can also modify the object orientation before placing it by holding the CTRL key and the left mouse button to rotate the object.
Ambient AI are animals or characters that are not part of the mission objective. Use them to add life and ambience in your map.
Animation points are attraction points that the AI in your map react to. The AI in the map will randomly select one animation point, move to that point and perform a specific animation at this location.

Use the Select Objects tool to define a precise selection that will stay locked until you cancel the selection. This can be useful for manipulating a complex set of objects without losing your selection. A red box indicates the locked state of the selection.
You can select multiple objects in a rectangular area by toggling the cursor, moving it to the top-left corner of the rectangle you wish to draw, holding the select action and then moving the cursor to the bottom-right corner. After releasing the select action, you will have selected all objects within that rectangle.
Use the Environment Settings tool to set the time of day, type of clouds, ambient light, ambient sounds, and the level of water in your map.

In the Map Properties menu, set the map name and mission objective and select a tag to display in the Map Browser.
This is also were you can take the snapshot that will be displayed in the Map Browser.
Use the Snapshot tool to take a representative picture of your map. This snapshot will appear in the map browser. Make sure you take a great picture of your map to attract players.

Use Add AI tool to place AI in the map at the location of the cursor.
There are two types of AI: Wave AI and Ambient AI. Wave AI relates directly to your mission objective. For example, in Assault, enemies will be treated as Wave AI, while in Hunt, Animals are treated as Wave AI. Ambient AI is peripheral to your objective. Ambient AI is meant to add to your map without affecting the mission objective and can make your map livelier, more visually appealing, or include tangential gameplay.
Wave AI are placed using the Add AI tool while Ambient AI can be placed using the Add tool.
Each map contains between one and five waves. Each wave is restricted by an AI budget. Ambient AI affects the budget of all the waves in the map, so be careful not to add too much Ambient AI since they will reduce the maximum amount of AI you can place in each wave.
The Trigger parameter determines at what point the current wave will begin relative to the previous wave. For example, in wave 2, if you set the Trigger at One Dead, wave 2 will begin once one enemy in wave 1 has been killed.
The Show parameter displays either all the AI in your map, or only the AI in your current wave. This setting is for display purposes only.
The Add Multiple Objects checkbox allows you to add multiple objects consecutively each time you click in your map.

Use the Ramp tool to create a linear ramp between two positions.
The Ramp tool can be useful to make higher terrains accessible, as well as evening out the terrain below a road, for example.
Use the Hole tool to completely remove sections of terrain. This can be used to then create caves and tunnels, by moving rocks or other appropriate objects in the hole to create an interior section.

Use the Bump tool to elevate or dig the terrain in the shape of a bump centered at the cursor. This is the simplest way to quickly modify the terrain.
Set the Speed parameter to control the speed of the modification of the terrain.

Use the Validation tool to make sure all the rules of a Mission are respected in order to play your map online.
Most of the time, this will consist of a required number of Player Spawn Points, Enemy or Animal AI, and other gameplay objects such as Outpost Alarms or Extraction Zones.
There are also more general rules that must be respected in every Mission, such as correctly placing spawn points and other game objects free of any collision with other objects, as well as respecting the given budgets.
You can quickly find an invalid object or the context of an error by simply selecting the error message.

The Chinook swims from the ocean back to freshwater where it spawns and then dies. It's sad, but you can never go home again.

Skunks will only spray when threatened, as they live life under the principle “don’t start none, won’t be none.”
Wild boar are like pigs only they party harder.
Rainbow Trout are the state's number one game fish and they never shut up about it. We get it, you won. Stop reminding us every day.
Unlike the Canadian Black Bear, these ones are loud, entitled, and don't apologize after killing you.
Bull Trout are an extremely sensitive species that don't tolerate high levels of sediment in their streams or any other environmental microaggressions.
A rat can survive for up to two years in the wild, but only about two days in the mob.
Duck penises are corkscrew shaped which is super handy for opening bottles of wine while camping.
Different types of trout are capable of mating and producing viable offspring, but they’ve remained distinct for thousands of years because trout are super racist.
Cougars have similar body types to house cats, only on a larger scale. Both types of cats are also giant assholes.
Reindeer and caribou are the same animal, only reindeer put on airs because they’re European.
These large birds are the main event of every Thanksgiving dinner and signal the beginning of insane sales where people die trying to get a “deal.”
The Ruffed Grouse is non-migratory bird that forgets the fact that at one time, one of their ancestors migrated from somewhere.
A turkey and a vulture had a regrettable one-night stand. One of them believed life begins at conception and look at that... a new species!
The porcupine mating ritual involves a male urinating on a female. If watersports is something that both parties are into, then let them do it.
Lake Trout can be difficult to find because of their preference for cold, dark, and murky lower depths. You can also find them trolling online forums.
The Kokanee are land-locked, and only live in freshwater. Like all salmon they die after spawning, which isn't such a bad way to go really.
Like a human, an adult deer has thirty-two teeth. Unlike a human, it will floss after every meal without fail.
You probably think bald eagles are bold, majestic hunters, but they actually eat trash and steal food from other birds. USA! USA! USA!
Moose are incredibly near-sighted, but are too cheap to pay for laser eye surgery.
Arctic Graylings can be identified by their colorful and very large dorsal fin. Fly that fin loud and proud, you majestic creatures.
Elk are vegetarian, but are known to eat meat such as nestlings or bird eggs on rare occasions. Which makes them the animal equivalent of your old college roommate.
Hares are adamant that they've never lost a race and warn everyone against believing FAKE NEWS from the Mainstream Tortoise Media.
The American Badger, like certain president, has tiny paws compared to other animals of a similar size.
The Largemouth Bass is similar to the Smallmouth Bass, only that the mouth is larger. Really, it's all there in the name.
They're the best there are at what they do, and what they do is secrete a foul smelling yellow liquid from their anal scent glands.

Paddlefish caviar is a hot commodity, but even if you harvest the eggs yourself, you can't take them out of state. Isn't that just like the government to think they have a say over someone else's eggs?
Wolves develop close relationships and strong social bonds. They are also known to hit the clubs after getting their pump on.
These omnivores are known to eat berries, fish, and, according to the Secretary of Education, children.
Rock Bass are fresh water fish who don't have a problem with being around human activity. They are completely unimpressed by everything we do. Everything.
A baby bison is called a "red dog" because the people who name things lack basic education. Also, humans slaughtered 50 million of them. 50 MILLION!
It is the male Bass that stays back and guards the eggs. They are the stay-at-home dads of the fish world.

The [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Sixth Sense[STYLE_END] perk will automatically tag enemies that are about to detect you. Allowing you to highlight the threat and eliminate it before you're detected.
Animals will also be less inclined to attack you.
The [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Adrenaline[STYLE_END] perk allows you to move faster in crouch, also you will auto tag enemies within 10 meters.

Earning survival instinct perks facilitates stealth actions and gives you an advantage over your enemy.
Perform [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]silent kills[STYLE_END] with melee attacks or silent weapons to [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]gain survival instinct perks[STYLE_END].
There are 4 Perks. [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Adrenaline[STYLE_END], [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Ghost[STYLE_END], [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Sixth Sense[STYLE_END] and [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Predator[STYLE_END].
If you get [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]detected[STYLE_END] you'll [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]lose[STYLE_END] all survival instinct perks.
Don't worry, you can perform new stealth kills to [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]regain[STYLE_END] them.
The [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Predator[STYLE_END] perk enables you to become an elite spotter, allowing you to tag enemies through walls using the binoculars, as well as auto tag enemies within 20 meters.
The [STYLE_DLCV_KEYWORD]Ghost[STYLE_END] perk reduces the noise you make while walking, sprinting and landing. Fall damage is also reduced.

{We are the Project at Eden’s Gate -- A family of refugees, cast from the world, bruised by rejection. Each of us has yearned for fellowship only to be deafened by hateful words, or struck by the blows of contemptuous fists. Each of us has carried labels designed to minimize, marginalize, dehumanize or separate us. Dear Matt,
I'm so sorry we couldn't convince you and Ann to make the big move and join us out here. I think you would have found the air bracing, and the quiet mornings restful for the mind. And of course Father Joseph's words are food for the soul. Maybe bring the kids out later in the year. I'm sure the quads would love it, and Marty is old enough to join Jacob's training program. May the Father bless you. Jody Holmes
Jacob’s hunting parties scour the region and drag anyone they catch to their training camps. He’ll break them and reforge them into an army loyal to the Father.
The Reaping: Taking What is Needed

John Seed marks those who are ready to be saved by the Father and welcomed into the church, on Father’s command. By baptizing those who he sees are ready to convert, he washes away their sins, and teaches them the power of Yes.

Oldest brother of the Seeds. In charge of TRAINING their militia up in the Whitetail Mountains.
Only thing he believes in is “SACRIFICE THE WEAK.” Seems to be running a few psychological experiments up north – all sorts of nightmare stories about people turning on one another at the drop of a hat…
Has been linked to the creation of the monster wolves up north the cult calls JUDGES.

Youngest of the Seed brothers and maybe the most sadistic.
In charge of “recruiting” for the cult – MARKING, CLEANSING, CONFESSION, ATONEMENT… those are the four steps he puts everyone through to become a member of Eden’s Gate – if they survive.
John tells everyone to accept “THE POWER OF YES” as a way to get his followers to do whatever the fuck he wants. Grade A psychopath.

Don’t know how she’s related – seems like she just showed up one day…
She'll spin you a sob story, but Faith is a LIAR and a MANIPULATOR. She’ll poison your mind with BLISS if you give her the chance.
Anyone who goes wandering into the Henbane River winds up either dead or "WALKING THE PATH" to become of one those brain-dead ANGELS doing all the cult’s hard labor.

United States District Court for the District of Montana
ARREST WARRANT
To: Any authorized law enforcement officer
YOU ARE COMMANDED to arrest and bring before a United States magistrate judge without unneccessary delay: JOSEPH SEED who is accused of suspicion of kidnapping with an intent to harm. (US LAW § 45-5-302)

April 27, 2015
Dad, I got your message. Good to hear they’re dropping the charges. We’ll try to come out for part of the summer – Ricky wants to show you how he’s riding without training wheels – but Anne’s got a lot of work at the college. I know how much it means to you, so we’ll try… only, please lay off the homeschooling talk, ok? It’s not right for me or Anne, and the school in South Street is one of the best. And let’s keep the “prepping” activities to a minimum. I know Ricky loves it, but it freaks Anne out.
Talk soon, Robbie

The Father has commanded John to begin filling Eden's Gates larders. He'll confine his sphere of influence to Holland Valley. His instructions are to focus on: Food and water Weapons and ammunition Trucks, cars, ATVs Fuel First aid kids and medicines Cleaning chemicals Toiletries Potential converts - to be sent to Jacob Potential workers - to be sent to Faith.
The community of Fall's End has resources in abundance.
Be safe. The Father will watch over you.
The Reaping: Calming Hearts and Minds

Leader of the Project at Eden’s Gate. He believes a great “COLLAPSE” is coming, and thinks of himself as a modern-day Noah.
Thinks God speaks to him -- told him to SAVE AS MANY SOULS AS HE CAN. Now that he's started THE REAPING, his followers are willing to die for him.
He's had his people build three massive BUNKERS to protect themselves when his "PROPHECY" comes true... The guy is an absolute nutjob.

The Father has commanded Faith to increase bliss production and output.
More harvests of flowers and refinement into the final product is required. Shipments need to be increased all along the river.

Richard "Dutch" Roosevelt served two nights in jail for contempt of court after contesting his right to collect rainwater in what the state has defined as reservoir. The Father has sent instructions to Jacob to protect Eden's Gate at all costs.
There will be people from the community who do not understand our message and teachings. Who are scared of us, or believe the governments lies, or think they know better.

Be courageous. The Father will watch over you.

{TX_PCButton_L_Mouse_Small} Select an object. {TX_PCButton_L_Mouse_Small} (Drag) Select all objects within a rectangle. {TX_PCButton_Shift} When selecting objects, adds them to the current selection. {TX_PCButton_L_Ctrl} When selecting objects, adds them to the current selection.

Use the Move Object mode to modify the position of the objects in your map.
Once you have selected one or more objects, click and hold the left mouse button on one of the arrows of the gizmo, in order to move the objects in the direction of the arrow you have selected.
You can also directly click on an object, and while holding the left mouse button, move it with your cursor. While moving a selection in this way, you can also hold the CTRL key to quickly rotate the selection instead of moving it.
You can clone the content of your selection by holding the SHIFT key and moving the selection using either of the two ways described above. The previous content will stay where it was.
You can move a selection by a fixed increment by enabling the Use snap grid option. Specify the increment by setting the Snap grid size parameter. The Snap with object size option will use increments that are the same as the object's bounding volume.
The Drop selection button will drop the objects until a collision is found. This can be useful for making sure an object matches either the ground or another object. If the Use center of selection option is activated, the object’s relative height will be preserved; otherwise each object will be dropped individually.

The Axis type parameter determines the orientation of the gizmo used for manipulating a selection. The Local option indicates the arrows will be oriented to match the orientation of its reference object. In that way, the arrows are in the direction of the object's own front, left, or up side. The World option indicates the arrows will always be in the same direction.

To snap objects, click on the source reference object with the left mouse button, and while holding it, drag towards the target reference object, after which you can release the button. Small points will appear to indicate the edge of the objects that will snap together.
The Snap Angle and Angle Direction parameters let you specify an angle at which you want the objects to be linked together.

Use the Add tool to place new objects, new gameplay objects, new AI, and new animation points in the map at the location of the cursor.
You can navigate through the different categories of objects by either using the drop down list, or by double-clicking on the folders.
You can also modify the object orientation before placing it by holding the CTRL key and the left mouse button to rotate the object.
Ambient AI are animals or characters that are not part of the mission objective. Use them to add life and ambience in your map.
Animation points are attraction points that the AI in your map react to. The AI in the map will randomly select one animation point, move to that point, and perform a specific animation at this location.

Use Smooth to soften out the terrain and even out irregularities.
Set the Speed parameter to control the speed at which the terrain will be smoothed out.

To prevent selecting objects by mistake, you can use the "Freeze selection" button to make the objects in your current selection unselectable. If you want to modify such objects again, simply use the "Unfreeze all objects" button.
You are about to save modifications to a Downloaded map. This operation will create a new file located in My Maps. The original file will remain unmodified.

Highlight a NPC, animal, or destructible object with the crosshair and press A to set it as a target in your map.
You can remove a target by pressing A again while having it highlighted with the crosshair.
The values in the top left corner of your screen indicate how many targets you have already set, and what your maximum amount of targets is.
You may lose any unsaved changes to the current map if you proceed. Do you wish to save the current map?

The Neighborhood selection checkbox will attempt to find the biggest object near your cursor and then select all the objects in its neighborhood automatically. For example, this can be useful for quickly selecting a house and all its content inside.

Use the Select mode to select a point by clicking on it. You can also select multiple objects by clicking and holding the left mouse button to define a rectangle of selection. When holding the SHIFT key, you can add points to your selection. When holding the CTRL key, you toggle the points to be either inside or outside of your selection.
While in Select mode, you can move selected points by clicking on one of them, and moving the mouse while holding the left mouse button.
Use the Draw mode to let the editor add points automatically by following the movement of your mouse while holding its left button. Note that this feature only works when no points exist, or when the action is started on an end point.
Use the Add mode to add a point by clicking and holding the left mouse button, either from a endpoint or from a segment.
Use the Remove mode to remove a point under the cursor while holding the left mouse button.
Currently in EXPLORE mode. Press ESC to open the Menu.

Use the Erosion tool to give terrain shapes a more natural look by simulating landslides starting from the area of your cursor.
Set the Density parameter to control the speed at which erosion occurs.
Set the Deformation parameter to control how much the terrain will be affected by the operation.
Set the Landslide parameter to control the strength at which the erosion will carve out the terrain.

The Use center of selection checkbox allows you to determine whether you want to move your selection using one of its objects as a reference, or by treating the selection as a whole, where the reference is the center of the selection. A white box will surround your selection to indicate it is being treated as a group.
Based on your center of selection, the pivot point will be centered on an individual object or the center of the bounding box accordingly.

Modifiers are adjustments you can make to the gameplay of your map. These can have a small or large effect depending on what modifiers you use alone or in combination. Try turning one or two modifiers on and testing your map to get a feel for how they work.
This is also where you can choose the startup weapon and skills.

Use the Rotate Object mode to modify the orientation of the objects in your map.
Once you have selected one or more objects, click and hold the left mouse button on one of the circles of the gizmo, in order to rotate the objects around the direction of the circle you have selected.
You can rotate a selection by a fixed increment by enabling Use snap angles. Specify the increment by setting the Snap angle parameter.
The "Reset tilt" button will reset the object’s orientation.

Just... how do I tell the town... without telling them about... my cravings.

If you were cold it would have been easier.
